var book = {
	"name": "1 Samuel",
	"numChapters": 31,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Efratini barima bi wɔ hɔ a ɔfiri Ramataim-sofim, Efraim bepɔ soɔ a ne din de Elkana, Suf ba, Tohu ba, Elihu ba, Yeroham ba.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔwɔ yerenom baanu, ɔbaako din de Hana, na ɔbaako din de Penina. Na Penina wɔ mma, nanso Hana deɛ, na ɔnni ba.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Daa afe ɔbarima yi firi ne kurom kɔ sɛ ɔrekɔsɔre na wabɔ afɔdeɛ ama asafo AWURADE wɔ Silo. Na ɛhɔ na Eli mma baanu Hofni ne Pinehas di AWURADE asɔfoɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na da a Elkana bɔ afɔdeɛ no, ɔma ne yere Penina ne ne mmammarima ne ne mmammaa nyinaa kyɛfa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Hana deɛ, ɔma no baanu kyɛfa, ɛfiri sɛ ɔdɔ Hana, nanso AWURADE ato ne yafunu mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ahi ara na na ne kora no yi no sɛ ɔbɛhuru ne boɔ, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE ato ne yafunu mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na saa na na ɔyɛ afe biara. Daa sɛ wɔforo kɔ AWURADE fie a, ɔyi no ahi saa; na ɔsu na ɔnnidi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ne kunu Elkana ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hana, adɛn na wosu, na adɛn na wonnidie, na adɛn na wo bo nnwoɔ? Menyɛ memma wo nsene mmammarima du anaa?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔdidiiɛ na wɔnom wieeɛ wɔ Silo no, Hana sɔreeɛ; nanso na Ɔsɔfoɔ Eli te adwa so AWURADE asɔredan ano aponnwa ho.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ne kra werɛ hoe, na ɔbɔɔ AWURADE mpaeɛ, na ɔde yea sui.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ bɔ sɛ: Asafo AWURADE, sɛ wohwɛ w’afenaa amanehunu na wokae me, na wo werɛ amfiri w’afenaa, na woma w’afenaa ɔbabanin a, ɛnneɛ mede no bɛma AWURADE ne nkwa nna nyinaa, na oyiwan biara renka ne ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ, ɔgu so rebɔ mpaeɛ AWURADE anim no, Eli hwɛɛ n’ano dinn;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na Hana rekasa n’akoma mu, na n’ano nko na ɔbesebese, na ne nne deɛ, wɔnte. Enti Eli buu no sɛ ɔsabofoɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛnna Eli ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Da bɛn na wobɛboro nsa akɔsie? Yi wo nsanom firi w’ani so.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Hana buaa sɛ: Dabi, me wura, meyɛ ɔbaa werɛhoni; na bobesa ne nsa biara deɛ, mennom bi, na mahwie me kra magu AWURADE anim;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> mfa w’abaawa nto ɔbaa huhuni bi ho, ɛfiri sɛ m’awerɛhoɔ ne m’ayamgya dodoɔ mu na makasa abɛsi sɛsɛɛ yi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnna Eli buaa sɛ: Fa asomdwoeɛ kɔ, na Israel Nyankopɔn mma wo adeɛ a wosrɛɛ no ne hɔ no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: Ma w’afenaa nnya w’anim adom. Ɛnna ɔbaa no sii mu kɔ kɔdidiiɛ, na n’anim nte sɛ kane no bio.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na wɔsɔree anɔpatutu kɔsɔree AWURADE anim, na wɔsane baa wɔn fie Rama. Na Elkana ne ne yere Hana daeɛ, na AWURADE kaee no;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na afe reduro no, na Hana anyinsɛn awo ɔbabarima, na ɔtoo no din Samuel, na ɔkaa sɛ: AWURADE hɔ na mesrɛɛ no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔbarima Elkana ne ne fiefoɔ nyinaa foro kɔɔ sɛ ɔrekɔbɔ afirinhyia afɔdeɛ de n’aboadeɛ akɔma AWURADE.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Hana deɛ, wankɔ, na ɔka kyerɛɛ ne kunu sɛ: Gye sɛ abɔfra no atwa nufoɔ ansa na mede no akɔ, na wakɔpue AWURADE anim, na watena hɔ daa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ne kunu Elkana ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Yɛ deɛ ɛyɛ wɔ w’ani so, tena hɔ kɔsi sɛ wobɛtwa no nufoɔ ansa; AWURADE asɛm ara na ɔmma no nnyina. Na ɔbaa no tenaa hɔ maa ne ba nufoɔ de kɔsii sɛ ɔtwaa no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔtwaa no no, ɔfaa no kaa ne ho de nantwinini a wadi mfeɛ mmiɛnsa ne esiam efa baako ne bobesa kotokuo ma de no baa AWURADE fie Silo. Na abɔfra no sua.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔkum nantwinini no, na wɔde abɔfra no brɛɛ Eli.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: O me wura, sɛ wo kra te aseɛ yi, me wura, mene ɔbaa a ɔbɛgyinaa wo nkyɛn ha yi bɔɔ AWURADE mpaeɛ no.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Abɔfra yi ho mpaeɛ na mebɔeɛ, na AWURADE ama me adeɛ a mesrɛɛ no ne hɔ no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Enti me deɛ, mede no mafɛm AWURADE; ne nna a ɔbɛtena aseɛ nyinaa mede no mama AWURADE. Na ɔsɔree AWURADE wɔ hɔ."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hana nso bɔɔ mpaeɛ sɛ: M’akoma di AWURADE mu ahurisie, AWURADE mu na wɔama m’abɛn soɔ; M’anomu atrɛ m’atamfoɔ so, ɛfiri sɛ m’ani gye wo nkwagyeɛ mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Obiara nyɛ Kronkron sɛ AWURADE, na obiara nni w’akyi, na Ɔbotan bi nni hɔ sɛ yɛn Nyankopɔn.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Monnkasa ahantan kasa bebree saa, mommma asɛm denden mmfiri mo anomu, na AWURADE ne Onyankopɔn a ɔhunu adeɛ nyinaa, na ɔno na ɔkari nneyɛɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ahoɔdenfoɔ tadua bubu, na mmerɛfoɔ deɛ, wɔde ahoɔden bɔ wɔn ho so;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Wɔn a wɔmee kɔdi aduane ho paa, na pititɔfoɔ kɔm gu; Obonini mpo awo nson, na deɛ ɔwɔ mma bebree no yɛ ɔhokwafoɔ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> AWURADE na ɔkum, na ɔma nkwa; ɔma wɔsiane kɔ Asamando, na ɔma wɔforo firi adi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> AWURADE ma obi di hia, na ɔma obi di yie; ɔbrɛ onipa ase, na ɔma onipa so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɔma mmɔborɔni so firi mfuturo mu, na ɔma ohiani so firi sumina so, sɛ ɔde no bɛtena mmapɔmma mu, na wama no anya animuonyam adwa so atena. Na asase nnyinasoɔ yɛ AWURADE dea, na ɔde wiase asi so.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɔhwɛ n’ahotefoɔ nan so, na abɔnefoɔ bɛtɔre mum esum mu; na ɛnyɛ ahoɔden so na onipa nam bɛdi nim.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> AWURADE atamfoɔ bɛwie pasaa, na ɔbɛma n’aprannaa abom ɔsoro agu wɔn so. AWURADE bɛbu asase ano atɛn; ɔde ahoɔden bɛma ne hene, na wama deɛ wasra no ngo no abɛn so.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Elkana kɔɔ ne fie Rama; na abɔfra no som AWURADE, Ɔsɔfoɔ Eli anim.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Eli mma no yɛ mma ahuhufoɔ; wɔmmu AWURADE.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na asɔfoɔ adeɛ a wɔyɛ ɔman no ne sɛ: Sɛ obi rebɔ afɔdeɛ a, wɔrenoa nam no, na ɔsɔfoɔ no somfoɔ aba, na ɔkura adinam a ano mmiɛnsa,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na ɔde abɛbɔ dadesɛn anaa ahina anaa ɛkyeɛ dadeɛ anaa kukuo no mu, na deɛ adinam no de bɛba nyinaa na ɔsɔfoɔ no afa; saa ara na na wɔyɛ Israelfoɔ a wɔba Silo hɔ nyinaa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nso wɔnnya nhyee sradeɛ no mmaa AWURADE no, na ɔsɔfoɔ no somfoɔ abɛka akyerɛ deɛ ɔrebɔ afɔdeɛ no sɛ: Ma nam na wɔnkɔtoto mma ɔsɔfoɔ; na ɔnnye wo hɔ nam a wɔanoa, na mmom ɛnam mono.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na sɛ ɔka sɛ: Ma wɔnhye sradeɛ no nwie ansa na woafa dodoɔ biara a wopɛ a, ɔsomfoɔ no ka sɛ: Dabi, na ma me bi prɛko, anyɛ saa a, mɛfa no ɔhyɛ so.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Enti mmeranteɛ no bɔne yɛɛ kɛse, AWURADE anim, ɛfiri sɛ nnipa no buu AWURADE aduane afɔdeɛ no animtia.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Samuel deɛ, ɔsom AWURADE anim; ɔyɛ abɔfra a wɔde nwera asɔfotadeɛ abɔ ne mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ne na pam batakari kumaa bi ma no, na ɔde kɔma no daa afe a ɔne ne kunu rekɔbɔ daa afe afɔdeɛ no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Eli hyira Elkana ne ne yere sɛ: AWURADE mma w’asefoɔ mfiri ɔbaa yi mu nsi akyɛdeɛ a ɔde ama AWURADE yi ananmu. Afei, wɔsim kɔ wɔn kurom.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na AWURADE bɛhwɛɛ Hana, na ɔnyinsɛnee, na ɔwoo mmammarima baasa ne mmammaa baanu. Na abɔfra Samuel no nyinii AWURADE anim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Afei na Eli abɔ akora, na ɔtee adeɛ a na ne mma de yɛ Israel nyinaa no nyinaa ne sɛdeɛ wɔne mmaa a na wɔbɛyɛ ahyiaeɛ ntomadan ano adwuma no da.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Adɛn nti na modi saa nsɛm yi? Na mete mo nsɛmmɔne yi firi ɔman yi nyinaa anomu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Dabi, me mma, na ɛnyɛ atenka pa na meteɛ yi; moma AWURADE man no fom.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sɛ obi yɛ onipa bi bɔne a, Onyankopɔn bɛpata ama no; na sɛ obi yɛ AWURADE bɔne a, hwan na ɔbɛpa kyɛw ama no? Nanso wɔantie wɔn agya nne, ɛfiri sɛ na AWURADE repɛ aku wɔn.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na abɔfra Samuel no kɔɔ so ara nyiniiɛ, na ɔnyaa anisɔ, AWURADE ne nnipa anim.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Nyankopɔn nipa bi baa Eli nkyɛn bɛka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Ɛnyɛ me ho adi na meyi mekyerɛɛ w’agya fie berɛ a wɔwɔ Misraim, Farao fie no,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> na meyii no Israel mmusuakuo nyinaa mu sɛ ɔmmɛdi me sɔfoɔ na ɔmmɔ m’afɔrebukyia so ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ na ɔnhye aduhwam na ɔnhyɛ asɔfotadeɛ no m’anim, na mede Israelfoɔ gya afɔdeɛ nyinaa memaa w’agya fie.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Adɛn nti na motiatia me kum afɔdeɛ ne m’aduane afɔdeɛ a mahyɛ sɛ wɔmmɔ no me tenabea no soɔ, na wodi wo mma ni sene me, sɛ mode me man Israel ayɛyɛdeɛ nyinaa mu adeɛ a ɛdi kan yɛ mo ho yie?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Enti AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn asɛm a ɔka nie: Mekae ampa sɛ: Wo fie ne w’agya fie nnante m’anim daa; nanso afei, deɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Ɛmpare me koraa; na wɔn a wɔdi me ni no, mɛdi wɔn ni, na wɔn a wɔbu me animtia no bɛbɔ ahohora.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hwɛ, nna bi reba a mɛtwa wo basa ne w’agya fie basa, na akɔkoraa bi renka wo fie.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na sɛ wohunu yie a Onyankopɔn bɛyɛ Israel no nyinaa a, ɛbɛma wo ho ahiahia wo wɔ me tenabea hɔ, ɛfiri sɛ akɔkoraa bi renka wo fie da biara da.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Nanso meremma onipa mmɔ wo m’afɔrebukyia ho, na wama w’ani ayɛ siamoo na wahyɛ wo kra awerɛhoɔ; na wo fie dodoɔ bɛwuwu wɔn mmeranteberɛ mu.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na yei nyɛ wo deɛ ɛbɛba wo mma baanu, Hofni ne Pinehas, soɔ no ho nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ: Da koro na wɔn baanu no bɛwuwuo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na mɛma ɔsɔfoɔ nokwafoɔ so mafa, ɔbɛyɛ deɛ ɛwɔ m’akoma ne me kra mu, na mɛkyekyere efie a ɛtim hɔ mama no, na wanante deɛ masra no no anim nna nyinaa.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na deɛ ɔbɛka wo fie no bɛba abɛkoto no agye dwetɛbena ne paanoo mua, na waka sɛ: Mesrɛ wo, fa me hyɛ asɔfoɔ adwuma no baako bi mu, na manya paanoo sini madi."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na abɔfra Samuel som AWURADE, Eli anim. Na AWURADE asɛm ho yɛ na nna no mu, na anisoadehunu ntaa mma.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɛberɛ no mu, ɛbaa sɛ da bi a Eli da ne daberɛ no, — nso na n’ani afiri aseɛ ayɛ kusukusu a ɔnhunu adeɛ yie, —",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na Nyankopɔn kanea no nnya nnumiiɛ, na Samuel da AWURADE asɔredan mu, deɛ Nyankopɔn adaka no sie hɔ;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> AWURADE frɛɛ Samuel, Samuel na ɔkaa sɛ: Menie.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔtuu mmirika kɔɔ Eli nkyɛn kɔkaa sɛ: Menie, na wofrɛɛ me. Na Eli kaa sɛ: Memfrɛɛ wo, sane kɔda. Na ɔkɔdae.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na AWURADE frɛɛ no bio, Samuel; na Samuel sɔre kɔɔ Eli nkyɛn kɔkaa sɛ: Menie, na wofrɛɛ me. Na Eli se: Memfrɛɛ wo, me ba, sane kɔda.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nso na Samuel nnya nhunuu AWURADE, na wɔnnya nyii AWURADE asɛm nkyerɛɛ no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na AWURADE kɔɔ so frɛɛ Samuel deɛ ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa; na ɔsɔre kɔɔ Eli nkyɛn kɔkaa sɛ: Menie, na wofrɛɛ me. Ɛnna Eli hunuu sɛ AWURADE na ɔrefrɛ abɔfra no,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> enti Eli ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Kɔda, na sɛ ɔfrɛ wo a, ka sɛ: AWURADE, kasa na w’akoa retie. Na Samuel kɔ kɔdaa ne daberɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na AWURADE ba bɛgyinaa hɔ frɛɛ sɛ kane no sɛ: Samuel, Samuel! Ɛnna Samuel se: Kasa, na w’akoa retie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Hwɛ, merebɛyɛ biribi Israel mu a obiara a ɔbɛteɛ no aso mmienu mu bɛyɛ no kyeoo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Da no, na mɛma adeɛ a maka atia Eli fie nyinaa aba mu firi mfitiaseɛ de kɔsi awieeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na maka makyerɛ no sɛ merebu ne fie atɛn akɔsi daa, amumuyɛ no nti, ɛfiri sɛ ɔnim sɛ ne mma retwetwe mmusuo, na wanka wɔn anim.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na enti maka ntam afa Eli fie ho sɛ: Sɛ wɔde okum afɔdeɛ ne aduane afɔdeɛ pata ma Eli fie mpo a, ɛrempepa wɔn amumuyɛ da biara da.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Samuel da kɔduruu anɔpa, na ɔhinihinii AWURADE fie apono no. Na Samuel suroo sɛ ɔbɛka adeɛ a ɔhunuiɛ no akyerɛ Eli.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna Eli frɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Me ba Samuel. Na ɔkaa sɛ: Menie.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: Asɛm bɛn na ɔka kyerɛɛ woɔ no? Nsi me asɛm no so. Sɛ wosi me asɛm a ɔka kyerɛɛ woɔ no nyinaa bi so a, Onyankopɔn ntua wo ka, na ɔmfa bi nka ho!",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna Samuel kaa nsɛm no nyinaa kyerɛɛ no, na wansi no bi so. Na ɔse: Ɛyɛ AWURADE, deɛ ɛyɛ n’ani soɔ no, ɔnyɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Samuel nyinii, na AWURADE dii n’akyi, na asɛm biara a Samuel kaeɛ no baa mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Israel nyinaa, ɛfiri Dan kɔsi Beer-seba hunuu sɛ wɔde Samuel asi hɔ sɛ ɔnyɛ AWURADE diyifoɔ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na AWURADE kɔɔ so yii ne ho adi Silo; na AWURADE nam AWURADE asɛm so yii ne ho kyerɛɛ Samuel wɔ Silo."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Samuel asɛm duruu Israel nyinaa nkyɛn. Na Israel tu kɔɔ sɛ wɔrekɔhyia Filistifoɔ ne wɔn akɔko; na wɔkɔkyeree nsraban Eben-eser, na Filistifoɔ nso bɛkyeree nsraban Afek.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Filistifoɔ no twaa mpasua hyiaa Israel, na ɔko no mu trɛe, na Israel dii nkoguo Filistifoɔ no anim, na wɔkumm mpasua no so nnipa bɛyɛ mpemnan.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔman no baa nsraban no mu no, Israel mpanin kaa sɛ: Adɛn nti na AWURADE ama yɛadi nkoguo nnɛ Filistifoɔ anim yi? Momma yɛnkɔfa AWURADE apam adaka no mfiri Silo mmra yɛn nkyɛn, na ɛmmra yɛn mu mmɛgye yɛn mfiri yɛn atamfoɔ nsam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna ɔman no soma maa wɔkɔɔ Silo kɔsoaa asafo AWURADE a ɔte Kerubim ntam no apam adaka no baeɛ, na Eli mma baanu no, Hofni ne Pinehas, na wɔwɔ Nyankopɔn apam adaka no ho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na AWURADE apam adaka no duruu nsram hɔ no, Israel nyinaa bɔɔ ose kɛseɛ maa asase wosoe.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Filistifoɔ tee osebɔ no, wɔkaa sɛ: Hebrifoɔ nsram osebɔ kɛseɛ yi aseɛ ne sɛn? Na wɔtee sɛ AWURADE adaka no aba nsraban no mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnna Filistifoɔ no suroeɛ, ɛnna wɔse: Onyankopɔn aba nsraban no mu. Na wɔkaa sɛ: Buei, yɛnnue! Na ɛmmaa saa pɛn.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Buei, yɛnnue! Hwan na ɔbɛyi yɛn afiri anyame atumfoɔ yi nsam? Yeinom ne anyame a wɔde haw nyinaa haa Misraim ɛserɛ so no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mo Filistifoɔ, monyɛ den, na monyɛ mmarima, na moansom Hebrifoɔ sɛdeɛ wɔsom mo no; enti monyɛ mmarima na monko.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Filistifoɔ no koeɛ, na Israel dii nkoguo, na wɔn nyinaa dwanedwane kɔɔ wɔn ntomadan mu. Na ɛyɛɛ okunkɛseɛ sɛ, na Israel mu nnipa a wɔnam anammɔn mu mpem aduasa totɔeɛ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Nyankopɔn adaka no, wɔfaeɛ, na Eli mma baanu no, Hofni ne Pinehas nso totɔeɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Benyaminni bi firi mpasua no mu tutuu mmirika baa Silo da no ara, na n’atadeɛ asunsuane, na dɔteɛ gu n’atifi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔduruiɛ no, na hwɛ, Eli te n’adwa so kwankyɛn rehwɛ kwan; na Nyankopɔn adaka no nti na ne bo ntɔ ne yam. Na ɔbarima no ba bɛkae, na kuro mu no nyinaa sui.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Eli tee esu no, ɔkaa sɛ: Hooyɛ gyegyeegye yi aseɛ ne sɛn? Na ɔbarima no yɛɛ ntɛm bɛka kyerɛɛ Eli.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nso na Eli adi mfeɛ aduɔkron nwɔtwe, na n’ani so ayɛ wisiwisi, na ɔnhunu adeɛ yie.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔbarima no ka kyerɛɛ Eli sɛ: Mene deɛ ɔfiri mpasua mu baeɛ no. Ɛnnɛ na mefiri mpasua no mu medwaneeɛ. Na ɔse: Asɛm no te sɛn, me ba?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔbɔfoɔ no buaa sɛ: Israel adwane Filistifoɔ anim, na wɔakum ɔman no mu nnipa pii nso, na wo mma baanu no, Hofni ne Pinehas, nso atotɔ, na Nyankopɔn adaka no, wɔafa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ, ɔbɔɔ Nyankopɔn adaka no din no, Eli firi n’adwa so muni faa n’akyi hwee ɛpono kɛseɛ no ho, na ne kɔn mu bui, na ɔwui, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔyɛ akɔkoraa a ne mu yɛ duru. Na wabu Israel atɛn mfeɛ aduanan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na n’ase, Pinehas yere, anyinsɛn a n’awoɔ reyɛ adu. Na ɔtee nsɛm no sɛ wɔafa Nyankopɔn adaka, na n’ase ne ne kunu awuwuo no, ɔkoto woe, na n’awoko yea kutaa no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɔrewu no, mmaa a wɔgyinagyina ne nkyɛn no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Nsuro, na ɔbarima na woawoɔ yi. Nanso wammua, na wammu asɛm no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔtoo abɔfra no din Ikabod, na ɔkaa sɛ: Fa a wɔafa Nyankopɔn adaka no ne n’ase ne ne kunu nti, animuonyam afiri Israel kɔ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Enti na ɔse: Animuonyam no afiri Israel so, ɛfiri sɛ wɔafa Nyankopɔn adaka no."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛberɛ a Filistifoɔ no faa Nyankopɔn adaka no, wɔde firi Eben-eser kɔɔ Asdod.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Filistifoɔ no de Nyankopɔn adaka no kɔɔ Dagon fie, na wɔde kɔsii Dagon nkyɛn.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, Asdodfoɔ sɔree anɔpatutu, na hwɛ, na Dagon ahwe ase a n’anim butu fam, AWURADE adaka no anim. Na wɔmaa Dagon so de no sii ne sibea.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ a wɔsɔree anɔpatutu no, na hwɛ, Dagon ahwe ase a n’anim butu fam, AWURADE adaka no anim, na Dagon tiri ne ne nsa mmienu abubu gugu aponnwa aseɛ deɛ no so, na Dagon kuntusini nko na aka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yei nti na Dagon asɔfoɔ ne wɔn a wɔba Dagon fie nyinaa ntia aponnwa aseɛ deɛ no so wɔ Asdod de bɛsi nnɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na AWURADE nsa yɛɛ duru Asdodfoɔ so, na ɔsɛee wɔn, na ɔde mpɔmpɔ bobɔɔ wɔn, Asdod ne ɛho nkurowa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na nnipa a wɔtete Asdod no hunuu sɛ ɛte saa no, wɔkaa sɛ: Mommma Israel Nyankopɔn adaka no nntena yɛn nkyɛn, ɛfiri sɛ ne nsa yɛ yɛn ne yɛn nyame Dagon so den papa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wɔsoma maa wɔkɔhyiahyiaa Filistifoɔ asafohene nyinaa baa wɔn nkyɛn kaa sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na yɛnyɛ Israel Nyankopɔn adaka no? Na wɔse: Wɔnsoa Israel Nyankopɔn adaka no nkɔ Gat. Na wɔsoaa Israel Nyankopɔn adaka no kɔɔ hɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔsoa kɔeɛ no, AWURADE nsa baa kuro no so, ebumbɔ kɛseɛ pa ara, na ɔbobɔɔ kuro no mufoɔ nketewa ne akɛseɛ nyinaa na mpɔmpɔ sisii wɔn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔmaa wɔde Nyankopɔn adaka no kɔɔ Ekron. Na wɔde Nyankopɔn adaka no duruu Ekron no, Ekronfoɔ no teaa mu sɛ: Wɔde Israel Nyankopɔn adaka no aba yɛn nkyɛn de rebɛku yɛn ne yɛn man!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔsoma maa wɔkɔhyiahyiaa Filistifoɔ asafohene nyinaa boaa ano, na wɔkaa sɛ: Momma wɔmfa Israel Nyankopɔn adaka no nsane nkɔ ne siberɛ, na ankuku yɛn ne yɛn man. Na owuo anikrakra baa kuro no mu nyinaa, na Nyankopɔn nsa yɛɛ duru wɔ wɔn so wɔ hɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na nnipa a wɔanwuo no, mpɔmpɔ sisii wɔn, na kuro no mufoɔ su a wɔsuiɛ no foro kɔɔ soro."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> AWURADE adaka no dii Filistifoɔ asase so abosome nson.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛnna Filistifoɔ frɛfrɛɛ asɔfoɔ ne akɔmfoɔ sɛ: Yɛnyɛ AWURADE adaka yi dɛn? Monkyerɛ yɛn adekodeɛ a yɛmfa nka ho nkɔ ne siberɛ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na wɔkaa sɛ: Sɛ morema wɔde Israel Nyankopɔn adaka no akɔ a, mommma wɔmmfa no hunu nnkɔ, na mmom momfa asodie afɔdeɛ nka ho nkɔ. Ɛno ansa na wɔbɛsa mo yadeɛ, na mobɛhunu deɛ enti a ne nsa mfiri mo soɔ yi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔkaa sɛ: Asodie afɔdeɛ bɛn na yɛmfa mma? Na wɔse: Momfa sika na wɔnyɛ no sɛ mpɔmpɔ nnum ne sika nkura nnum, sɛdeɛ Filistifoɔ asafohene ano sie, ɛfiri sɛ ɔhaw koro no ara na ɛwɔ mo nyinaa ne mo asafohene soɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Enti monyɛ mo mpɔmpɔ no nsɛsoɔ ne mo nkura a wɔsɛe mo asase no nsɛsoɔ, na momfa animuonyam mma Israel Nyankopɔn: Ebia ne nsa bɛyɛ hare afiri mo ne mo anyame ne mo asase so.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na adɛn nti na moyɛ mo akoma denden sɛdeɛ Misraimfoɔ ne Farao yɛɛ wɔn akoma denden no? Ɛnyɛ sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ wɔn adeɛ wieeɛ no ansa na wɔregya wɔn kwan ama wɔakorɔ?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na afei monyɛ teaseɛnam foforɔ, na momfa anantwibereɛ mmienu a wɔma nufoɔ a kɔnnua nkɔɔ wɔn so da, na momfa anantwie no nsesa teaseɛnam no, na montete wɔn mma mfiri wɔn ho nkɔ fie;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na momfa AWURADE adaka no nsi teaseɛnam no so, na momfa sika nnwinneɛ a mode rekɔyɛ asodie afɔdeɛ ama no no ngu adakawa mu mfa nsi nkyɛn, na monnya no kwan na ɛnkɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na monhwɛ, sɛ ɛfa ɛno ara ne hyeɛ so kwan foro kɔ Bet-semes a, ɛnneɛ na ɔno na ɔyɛ yɛn bɔne kɛseɛ yi; na sɛ anyɛ saa a, na yɛahunu sɛ ɛnyɛ ɔno na ne nsa ha yɛn, na asiane bi na asiane yɛn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na nnipa no yɛɛ saa, na wɔfaa anantwie mmienu a wɔma nufoɔ de wɔn sesaa teaseɛnam no, na wɔtoo wɔn mma mu wɔ efie;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na wɔde AWURADE adaka no sii teaseɛnam no so, na wɔde adakawa a sika nkura ne wɔn mpɔmpɔ nsɛsoɔ no wɔ mu no kaa ho.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na anantwie no faa kwan tee kɔɔ Bet-semes kwan so; wɔnam ɔtempɔn koro so, na wɔrekorɔ no na wɔresu, na wɔammane ankɔ nifa anaa benkum; na Filistifoɔ asafohene no dii wɔn akyi kɔduruu Bet-semes hyeɛ so.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nso na Bet-semesfoɔ retwa wɔn ayuo bonhwa mu; na wɔmemaa wɔn ani so hunuu adaka no, na ne hunu no yɛɛ wɔn anigyeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na teaseɛnam no duruu Bet-semesni Yosua afuo mu na ɛgyinaa hɔ; nso na ɔbo kɛseɛ bi wɔ hɔ; na wɔpaepaee teaseɛnam no nnua, na wɔde anantwie no bɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ maa AWURADE.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Lewifoɔ no yii AWURADE adaka no ne adakawa a ɛka ho a sika nnwinneɛ no wɔ mu no sisii ɔbo kɛseɛ no so; na Bet-semesfoɔ no bobɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ na wɔkunkum okum afɔdeɛ da no ara maa AWURADE.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Filistifoɔ asafohene baanum no hunuiɛ no, wɔsane kɔɔ Ekron da no ara.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na yeinom ne sika mpɔmpɔ a Filistifoɔ de yɛɛ asodie afɔdeɛ de brɛɛ AWURADE no: Asdod deɛ baako, Gasa deɛ baako, Askelon deɛ baako, Gat deɛ baako, Ekron deɛ baako;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ne sika nkura no, sɛdeɛ Filistifoɔ nkuro a ɛyɛ asafohene baanum no deɛ ano sie no, ɛfiri nkuro a wɔatoto ho afasuo soɔ de kɔsi petee mu nkuraa so. Na adanseɛ ne ɔbo kɛseɛ a wɔde AWURADE adaka no sii soɔ no, na ɛwɔ Bet-semesni Yosua afuo mu bɛduru nnɛ da yi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔkumm Bet-semesfoɔ no mu bi sɛ wɔahwɛ AWURADE adaka no mu, na ɔkumm ɔman no mu nnipa aduɔson ne nnipa mpem aduonum. Na ɔman no dii abooboo sɛ AWURADE de ekum kɛseɛ akum ɔman no mu nnipa bie.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Bet-semesfoɔ no kaa sɛ: Hwan na ɔbɛtumi agyina AWURADE, Onyankopɔn kronkronni yi anim, na hwan nkyɛn na ɔmfiri yɛn nkyɛn nkorɔ?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔsomaa abɔfoɔ maa wɔkɔɔ Kiriat-yearimfoɔ nkyɛn sɛ: Filistifoɔ de AWURADE adaka no aba, na mommɛfa nkɔ mo nkyɛn."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Kiriat-yearimfoɔ ba bɛfaa AWURADE adaka no de foro kɔɔ Abinadab fie, kokoɔ no so, na wɔdwiraa ne ba Eleasa sɛ ɔnhwɛ AWURADE adaka no so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na adaka no baa Kiriat-yearim no, ɛkyɛree wɔ hɔ; ɛdii mfirinhyia aduonu. Na Israel fie nyinaa dii abooboo hwehwɛɛ AWURADE akyiri kwan.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Israel fie nyinaa sɛ: Sɛ mode mo akoma nyinaa resane aba AWURADE nkyɛn a, ɛnneɛ monyi ananafoɔ anyame ne Astarot no mfiri mo mu, na monsiesie mo akoma mma AWURADE, na monsom ɔno nko ara, na ɔbɛyi mo Filistifoɔ nsam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna Israelfoɔ no yii Baalim ne Astarot, na wɔsomm AWURADE nko ara.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Samuel kaa sɛ: Monhyia Israel nyinaa mmra Mispa, na memmɔ AWURADE mpaeɛ memma mo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔbɛhyiaa wɔ Mispa, na wɔsaa nsuo hwie guu AWURADE anim, na wɔdii abuada da no, na wɔkaa no ɛhɔ sɛ: Yɛayɛ AWURADE bɔne. Na Samuel buu Israelfoɔ atɛn Mispa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Filistifoɔ tee sɛ Israelfoɔ akɔhyia Mispa no, Filistifoɔ asafohene foro baa Israel so. Na Israelfoɔ teeɛ no, wɔsuroo Filistifoɔ no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Nnyae osu a woresu afrɛ AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn ama yɛn no, na ɔnnye yɛn mfiri Filistifoɔ nsam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Samuel faa odwanten ba a ɔnum de no bɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ mu maa AWURADE; na Samuel su frɛɛ AWURADE maa Israel, na AWURADE gyee no so.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Samuel rebɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no, Filistifoɔ no twe pinii sɛ wɔne Israel rebɛko, na AWURADE paepaee aprannaa akɛseɛ guu Filistifoɔ no so da no, na ɔkaa wɔn gui maa wɔtotɔe Israel anim.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Israel mmarima firii adi firii Mispa kɔpamm Filistifoɔ no, na wɔkunkumm wɔn ara kɔsii Bet-kar ase.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna Samuel faa ɔboɔ baako de sii Mispa ne Sen ntam, na ɔtoo no din Eben-eser kaa sɛ: Ɛha na AWURADE aboa yɛn abɛsie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔbrɛɛ Filistifoɔ no ase, na wɔankɔ so amma Israel hyeɛ mu bio; na AWURADE nsa daa Filistifoɔ so Samuel nna nyinaa mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔdanee nkuro a Filistifoɔ agye no Israel nsam no maa Israel, ɛfiri Ekron kɔsi Gat, na ɛho asase nso, Israel gyee Filistifoɔ nsam. Na asomdwoeɛ baa Israelfoɔ ne Amorifoɔ ntam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Samuel buu Israel atɛn ne nkwa nna nyinaa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na afe afe biara na ɔkyini kɔ Betel ne Gilgal ne Mispa, na ɔbu Israel nyinaa atɛn nkuro yi nyinaa mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔsane ba Rama, na ɛhɔ na na ne fie wɔ, na ɔbu Israel atɛn hɔ; na ɔsii afɔrebukyia wɔ hɔ maa AWURADE."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɛberɛ a Samuel bɔɔ akora no, ɔde ne mma sisii Israel so atemmufoɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na n’abakan din de Yoel, na deɛ ɔka ho no de Abiya; wɔyɛɛ atemmufoɔ wɔ Beer-seba.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nanso ne mma amfa n’akwan so, na wɔmane kɔdii mfasoɔ akyi, na wɔgyegyee adanmudeɛ, na wɔbubuu ntɛnkyea.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna Israel mpanimfoɔ nyinaa hyia baa Samuel nkyɛn wɔ Rama",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bɛka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, woabɔ akora, na wo mma mfa w’akwan so. Afei si ɔhene ma yɛn na ɔnni yɛn so te sɛ amanaman nyinaa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na asɛm no ansɔ Samuel ani sɛ wɔkaa sɛ: Ma yɛn ɔhene na ɔnni yɛn so no. Na Samuel bɔɔ AWURADE mpaeɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Tie deɛ ɔman no seɛ ne deɛ wɔka kyerɛ woɔ no nyinaa, ɛfiri sɛ ɛnyɛ wo na wɔapo woɔ, na me na wɔapo me, sɛ mennni wɔn so hene.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wɔn nneyɛɛ a wɔayɛ nyinaa firi da a meyii wɔn Misraim baeɛ de bɛduru nnɛ yi de agyaa me akɔsom anyame foforɔ no, saa ara na wɔreyɛ wo nso yi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Enti, afei tie wɔn; na kasa kyerɛ wɔn, na kyerɛ wɔn ɔhene a ɔbɛdi wɔn soɔ no atemmudeɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Samuel kaa AWURADE nsɛm no nyinaa kyerɛɛ ɔman no a wɔbisaa ne hɔ ɔhene no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: Yei ne ɔhene a ɔbɛdi mo soɔ no atemmudeɛ: Ɔbɛfa mo mmammarima de wɔn akɔ ne nteaseɛnam ne n’apɔnkɔsotefoɔ mu, na wama wɔatu mmirika adi ne nteaseɛnam anim sɛ awɛmfoɔ,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na ɔde wɔn asisi mpempem so asafohene ne aduonum so asafohene afa, na wama wɔadɔ n’asase na wɔatwa ne nnɔbaeɛ, na wɔayɛ n’akodeɛ ne ne nteaseɛnam ho adeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔbɛfa mo mmammaa ayɛ adufrafoɔ ne soodofoɔ ne paanootofoɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔbɛfa mo mfuo ne mo bobe nturo mu deɛ ɛyɛ de ama ne nkoa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔbɛgye mo ayufuo ne bobe nturo mu aba mu ntotosoɔ du du de ama gyaasefoɔ ne ne nkoa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔbɛfa mo nkoa ne mo mfenaa, ne mo mmeranteɛ a wɔn ho tua wɔn ho, ne mo mfunumu de ayɛ n’adwuma.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɔbɛgye mo nnwan mu ntotosoɔ du du. Na mobɛyɛ ne nkoa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na da no, mo hene a moayi no adi mo soɔ no nti mobɛsu afrɛ, nanso AWURADE remmua mo da no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔman no ampene sɛ wɔtie Samuel, na wɔkaa sɛ: Dabi, na ɔhene ara na ɔnni yɛn soɔ,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na yɛn nso yɛnyɛ sɛ amanaman nyinaa, na yɛn hene no mmu yɛn atɛn, na ɔmfiri adi nni yɛn anim nni ako mma yɛn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Samuel tee ɔman no nsɛm nyinaa no, ɔka guu AWURADE aso mu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Tie wɔn, na si hene ma wɔn. Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Israelfoɔ nyinaa sɛ: Monkɔ mo nkuro mu."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Benyaminni bi wɔ hɔ a ne din de Kis a ɔyɛ Benyamin aseni, Afia ba, Bekorat ba, Seror ba, Abiel ba, ɔbarima a ɔyɛ ɔdefoɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔwɔ ɔbabarima bi a ne din de Saulo, aberanteɛ a ne ho yɛ fɛ. Na Israelfoɔ mu biara nsene no ahoɔfɛ. Ɛfiri ne mmatiri so rekorɔ no, ɔware sene obiara, ɔman no mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Saulo agya Kis mfunumu yerae. Na Kis ka kyerɛɛ ne ba Saulo sɛ: Fa asomfoɔ no mu baako ka wo ho, na sɔre kɔhwehwɛ mfunumu no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔkɔfaa Efraim bepɔ so, na wɔfaa Salisa asase so, nanso wɔanhu wɔn; na wɔfaa Saalim asase so, nanso na wɔnni hɔ; na wɔfaa Benyamin asase so, nanso wɔanhu wɔn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔduruu Suf asase soɔ no, Saulo ka kyerɛɛ abɔfra a ɔka ne ho no sɛ: Bra ma yɛnsane nkɔ, na m’agya annyae mfunumu no deɛ ammɛdi yɛn ho dadwene.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nanso ɔsomfoɔ no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, Nyankopɔn nipa bi wɔ kuro yi mu, na ɔyɛ onipa a n’anim yɛ nyam, deɛ ɔka nyinaa ba mu. Ma yɛnkɔ hɔ, ebia ɔbɛka yɛn ɔkwan a yɛrekorɔ yi ho asɛm bi akyerɛ yɛn.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Saulo bisaa ne somfoɔ no sɛ: Hwɛ, yɛkɔ a, ɛdeɛn na yɛde bɛkɔ akɔma ɔbarima no? Na paanoo asa wɔ yɛn adeɛ mu, na ayɛyɛdeɛ biara nni hɔ a yɛde rekɔma Nyankopɔn nipa no; ɛdeɛn na yɛwɔ?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na abɔfra no buaa Saulo bio sɛ: Hwɛ, mekura dwetɛ dwetɛbena abupɛn nnan mu baako, na mede bɛma Nyankopɔn nipa no, na wakyerɛ yɛn yɛn kwan.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> (Akane no, Israel, sɛ obi rekɔbisa Nyankopɔn hɔ adeɛ a, ɔka sɛ: Mommra mma yɛnkɔ ɔdehunufoɔ no nkyɛn; na deɛ nnɛ wɔfrɛ no odiyifoɔ no, akane no na wɔfrɛ no ɔdehunufoɔ).",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna Saulo ka kyerɛɛ n’abɔfra no sɛ: Ɔsɛmpa, bra ma yɛnkɔ. Na wɔkɔɔ kuro a Nyankopɔn nipa no wɔ mu no mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔreforo kuro no aforoeɛ no, wɔhunuu mmabaa a wɔrefiri abɛsa nsuo. Na wɔbisaa mmabaa no sɛ: Ɔdehunufoɔ no wɔ hɔ anaa?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔbuaa wɔn sɛ: Ɔwɔ hɔ, hwɛ, ɔwɔ w’anim ha yi ara. Yɛ ntɛm, na ɛnnɛ waba kuro no mu, na ɔman no bɔ afɔdeɛ nnɛ, sorɔnsorɔnbea hɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Moduru kuro no mu ara pɛ a, mobɛhu no ansa na wakɔ sorɔnsorɔnbea hɔ akɔdidi; ɛfiri sɛ ɔman no nnidi kɔsi sɛ ɔbɛba, na ɔno na ɔhyira afɔdeɛ no soɔ ansa na wɔn a wɔahyia wɔn no adidi. Enti momforo nkɔ, na berɛ yi ara na mobɛhu no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔforo kɔɔ kuro no mu. Wɔduruu kuro no mu no, hwɛ, na Samuel refiri adi abɛhyia wɔn aforo akɔ sorɔnsorɔnbea hɔ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nso na AWURADE ayi Samuel asotire da koro ansa na Saulo reba sɛ:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɔkyena sɛsɛɛ berɛ yi mu mɛsoma ɔbarima bi afiri Benyamin asase so aba wo nkyɛn, na sra no ngo si no me man Israel so hene, na ɔnnye me man mfiri Filistifoɔ nsam; na mahunu me man, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn su aduru me nkyɛn.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Samuel hunuu Saulo no, AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, onipa a mesee wo sɛ ɔbɛdi me man soɔ no nie.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Saulo twe pinii Samuel kuro pono no ano kaa sɛ: Mesrɛ wo, kyerɛ me deɛ ɔdehunufoɔ no fie wɔ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Samuel buaa Saulo sɛ: Mene ɔdehunufoɔ no. Foro di m’anim kɔ sorɔnsorɔnbea hɔ, na mo ne me bɛdidi nnɛ, na adeɛ kye a, magya mo kwan; na mɛka wo deɛ ɛwɔ w’akomam nyinaa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wo mfunumu a wɔyeraa nnansa ne nnɛ no deɛ, mfa w’adwene nto so, na wɔahu wɔn. Na hwan na Israel aboɔdenneɛ nyinaa wɔ no? Ɛnyɛ wo ne w’agya fie nyinaa dea anaa?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Saulo buaa sɛ: Ɛnyɛ Benyaminni ne me na memfiri Israel mmusuakuo mu ketewa no mu, na ɛnyɛ m’abusua ne Benyamin abusuakuo mu mmusua nyinaa mu ketewa anaa? Na adɛn nti na woka saa asɛm yi kyerɛ me?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Samuel faa Saulo ne ne somfoɔ no, na ɔde wɔn kɔɔ adidiiɛ, na ɔmaa wɔn atenaeɛ wɔ wɔn a wɔahyia wɔn no ti: Wɔbɛyɛ nnipa aduasa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ osoodoni no sɛ: Fa nankum a mesee wo sɛ fa sie no bra.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na soodoni no kɔfaa ɔsrɛ ne deɛ ɛwɔ ho no de bɛsii Saulo anim; na Samuel kaa sɛ: Hwɛ, deɛ wɔagya nie; fa si w’anim di, ɛfiri sɛ wɔde asie ama wo berɛ a wo ne ɔman no bɛdidie. Na Saulo ne Samuel didii da no.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔfiri sorɔnsorɔnbea hɔ siane baa kuro no mu, na ɔne Saulo kasaa ɛdan atifi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na wɔsɔree nhema; na adeɛ rekye no, Samuel frɛɛ Saulo ɛdan atifi sɛ: Sɔre na mennya wo kwan. Na Saulo sɔree, na wɔn baanu no, ɔno ne Samuel, firii adi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Wɔsiane kɔduruu kurotia no, Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Ka kyerɛ aberanteɛ no na ɔmmɛsene nni yɛn anim nkɔ, na ɔsene kɔ a; wo deɛ, gyina ha na menka wo nhyehyɛɛ a Onyankopɔn wɔ ma wo."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna Samuel faa ngo toa hwie guu n’atifi, na ɔfee n’ano kaa sɛ: Ɛnyɛ sra na AWURADE asra wo asi n’agyapadeɛ so hene ne ɔman Israel so anaa? Na wobɛdi AWURADE nkurɔfoɔ so hene, na woagye wɔn afiri wɔn atamfoɔ a wɔatwa wɔn ho ahyia no nsam. Na yei bɛyɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ama wo sɛ AWURADE asi wo hene wɔ n’agyapadeɛ so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Wofiri me nkyɛn nnɛ rekorɔ yi, wobɛto mmarima baanu wɔ Selsa, Rahel da so, Benyamin hyeɛ so, na wɔbɛka akyerɛ wo sɛ: Mfunumu a wokɔhwehwɛɛ wɔn no, wɔahu wɔn, na hwɛ, w’agya agyae mfunumu no ho dwene, na mo so na ne dadwen abɛsie sɛ: Menyɛ dɛn me ba yi ho?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na wofiri hɔ kɔ w’anim, na woduru Tabor dupɔn no ho a, mmarima baasa a wɔrekɔ Nyankopɔn nkyɛn Betel bɛhyia wo hɔ, ɔbaako so mmirekyie mmiɛnsa, na ɔbaako so paanoo mua mmiɛnsa, na ɔbaako so bobesa ahina ma.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔbɛkyea wo, na wɔama wo paanoo mmienu na woagye wɔ wɔn nsam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛno akyiri no, wobɛduru Gibea-elohim, wɔ deɛ Filistifoɔ bansifoɔ wɔ no; na ɛbɛba sɛ woduru kuro no mu hɔ a, wobɛhyia adiyifoɔ asafo a wɔresiane afiri sorɔnsorɔnbea hɔ, na bɛnta ne mpintin ne mmɛn ne asankuo di wɔn anim; na wɔrehyɛ nkɔm.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na AWURADE honhom bɛsi wo so, na wo ne wɔn ahyɛ nkɔm, na woadane ayɛ onipa foforɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ yi ba mu ma wo a, yɛ deɛ wo nsa bɛso soɔ fa, na Onyankopɔn di w’akyi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na di m’anim siane kɔ Gilgal, na hwɛ, me nso meresiane maba wo nkyɛn mabɛbɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ. Tena hɔ twɛn nnanson kɔsi sɛ mɛba wo nkyɛn mabɛkyerɛ wo deɛ yɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔdanee ne ho sɛ ɔrefiri Samuel nkyɛn akorɔ no, Onyankopɔn maa no akoma foforɔ; na nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ yi nyinaa baa mu da no ara.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔduruu kokoɔ no so hɔ no, hwɛ, adiyifoɔ asafo bɛhyiaa no, na Nyankopɔn honhom bɛsii ne so, na ɔhyɛɛ nkɔm wɔ wɔn mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔn a wɔni no kane no nyinaa hunuu no sɛ ɔrehyɛ nkɔm adiyifoɔ mu no, nkurɔfoɔ no sesee wɔn ho wɔn ho sɛ: Ɛdeɛn ne deɛ ayɛ Kis ba no yi? Saulo nso fra adiyifoɔ no mu anaa?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na obi a ɔfiri hɔnom buaa sɛ: Na wɔn kannifoɔ ne hwan? Enti ɛdanee abebusɛm sɛ: Saulo nso fra adiyifoɔ no mu anaa?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔwiee nkɔmhyɛ no, ɔbaa sorɔnsorɔnbea hɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Saulo agya nua bisaa no ne somfoɔ no sɛ: Ɛhe na mokɔeɛ? Na ɔse: Yɛkɔhwehwɛɛ mfunumu no na yɛhunuu sɛ wɔnni hɔ no, yɛkɔɔ Samuel nkyɛn.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Saulo agya nua no kaa sɛ: Ka me deɛ Samuel ka kyerɛɛ mo no!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ n’agya nua no sɛ: Ɔkaa no pefee kyerɛɛ yɛn sɛ wɔahunu mfunumu no. Na ahennie no ho asɛm a Samuel kaeɛ no deɛ, wanka ankyerɛ no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Samuel hyiaa ɔman no baa AWURADE nkyɛn Mispa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ Israelfoɔ no sɛ: Sɛdeɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Me na meyii Israel firi Misraim baeɛ, na megyee mo Misraim nsam ne ahennie a ɛhyɛɛ mo soɔ nyinaa nsam.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mo deɛ, ɛnnɛ moapo mo Nyankopɔn a ɔne deɛ ɔgyee mo mo amaneɛ ne mo ahohia nyinaa mu no, na mose no sɛ: Dabi, na si yɛn so hene. Na afei mommɛgyina AWURADE anim sɛdeɛ mo mmusuakuo ne mo mpempem dodoɔ teɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Samuel maa Israel mmusuakuo no nyinaa twe pinii, na wɔtwee ntoto maa ɛbɔɔ Benyamin abusuakuo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔmaa Benyamin abusuakuo no pinkyɛe, sɛdeɛ ne mmusua no teɛ; na wɔtwee ntonto maa ɛbɔɔ Matri abusua, na ɛbɔɔ Kis ba Saulo. Nanso wɔhwehwɛɛ no no, wɔanhu no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wɔkɔbisaa AWURADE bio sɛ: Onipa no bɛnya aba anaa? Na AWURADE se: Hwɛ, wakɔhunta nnoɔma no mu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔtutuu mmirika kɔfaa no firii hɔ. Na ɔbɛgyinaa ɔman no mu no, na ɔware sene ɔman no nyinaa firi ne mmatiri so kɔ soro.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no nyinaa sɛ: Monhwɛ deɛ AWURADE ayi no, na obiara nte sɛ ɔno, ɔman yi nyinaa mu. Na ɔman no nyinaa bɔɔ ose sɛ: Ɔhene tiri nkwa!",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ɛnna Samuel kaa ahennie no ho nhyehyɛɛ kyerɛɛ ɔman no, na ɔtwerɛ hyɛɛ nwoma mu de too AWURADE anim. Na Samuel gyaa ɔman no nyinaa kwan maa wɔkɔɔ wɔn afie.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Saulo nso kɔɔ ne fie Gibea, na ɛdɔm no mu akokoɔdurufoɔ binom a Onyankopɔn aka wɔn akoma no ne no kɔe.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na nnipa hunu bi kaa sɛ: Oyi bɛyɛ dɛn na wagye yɛn? Na wɔbuu no animtia, na wɔamfa ayɛyɛdeɛ ammrɛ no. Na ɔyɛɛ sɛ deɛ ɔnteɛ."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Amonni Nahas foro ba bɛkyeree Yabes-gilead so nsraban. Na Yabes mmarima nyinaa ka kyerɛɛ Nahas sɛ: Ɛne yɛn mpam na yɛnsom wo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Amonni Nahas no ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Ansa na me ne mo bɛpam no, gye sɛ metutu mo ani nifa nyinaa na mede mayɛ ahohora mato Israel nyinaa so.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yabes mpanimfoɔ no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ma yɛn nnanson, na yɛnsomasoma abɔfoɔ nkɔ Israel ahyeɛ nyinaa so, na sɛ obi nni hɔ a ɔbɛgye yɛn a, yɛafiri adi aba wo nkyɛn.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna abɔfoɔ no baa Gibea, faako a Saulo firi bɛkaa asɛm no ɔman no aso mu; na ɔman no nyinaa memaa wɔn nne so sui.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na hwɛ, na Saulo di anantwie akyi firi afuo mu reba; na Saulo kaa sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na ayɛ ɔman yi na wɔresu yi? Na wɔkaa Yabesfoɔ nsɛm no kyerɛɛ no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Saulo tee nsɛm yi no, AWURADE honhom sii ne so, na ne bo fuu kɛse.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔfaa anantwie mpamho twitwaa wɔn asinasini de hyehyɛɛ abɔfoɔ no nsa soma maa wɔkɔɔ Israel asase nyinaa so kɔkaa sɛ: Obiara a wamfiri adi ammɛdi Saulo ne Samuel akyire no, sɛ wɔbɛyɛ n’anantwie nie. Ɛnna AWURADE ho hu tɔɔ ɔman no soɔ, na wɔfiri baa sɛ onipa baako.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔkan wɔn Besek, na Israelfoɔ no ano si mpem ahasa, na Yuda mmarima si mpem aduasa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ abɔfoɔ a wɔbaeɛ no sɛ: Sei na monkɔka nkyerɛ Yabes-gileadfoɔ no nie: Ɔkyena a owia mu reyɛ den no, mobɛnya ɔgyeɛ. Na abɔfoɔ no ba bɛka kyerɛɛ Yabesfoɔ no, wɔn ani gyee.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Yabesfoɔ no kaa sɛ: Ɔkyena yɛbɛfiri adi aba mo nkyɛn, na moayɛ yɛn sɛdeɛ ɛyɛ mo ani soɔ nyinaa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, Saulo buu ɔman no mu asafokuo mmiɛnsa na wɔkɔɔ nsraban no mu anɔpa dasuo mu, na wɔkunkumm Amon kɔduruu awia ketee. Na wɔn a ɛkaeɛ no bɔ petee a anka wɔn mu baanu mpo wɔ faako.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna ɔman no ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Hwan na ɔkaa sɛ: Saulo na ɔrebɛdi yɛn so hene yi, no? Fa nnipa no bra ma yɛnku wɔn.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Saulo kaa sɛ: Wɔnnkum obiara nnɛ da yi, ɛfiri sɛ ɛnnɛ AWURADE ayɛ nkwagyedeɛ Israel mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Mommra mma yɛnkɔ Gilgal, na yɛnkɔyɛ ahennie no foforɔ wɔ hɔ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔman no nyinaa kɔɔ Gilgal, na wɔkɔsii Saulo hene AWURADE anim wɔ Gilgal; na wɔbobɔɔ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ AWURADE anim wɔ hɔ. Na Saulo ne Israel mmarima nyinaa ani gyee hɔ sɛ biribi."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Israel nyinaa sɛ: Hwɛ, matie mo, sɛdeɛ moka kyerɛɛ me no nyinaa, na masi mo so hene.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na afei, hwɛ, ɔhene no na ɔdi mo anim yi. Na me deɛ, mabɔ akora na mafu dwono, na me mma nso, hwɛ, wɔne mo na ɛwɔ hɔ; na me deɛ, mefiri me mmɔfraase na manante mo anim mabɛduru nnɛ da yi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hwɛ, menie, monni me adanseɛ AWURADE ne deɛ wasra no yi anim, hwan nantwie na mafa? Na hwan afunumu na mafa? Na hwan na madi no amim? Na hwan na mahyɛ ne soɔ anaa hwan hɔ na magye adanmudeɛ na mede mamua m’ani mama no? Na mennane memma mo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔse: Wonnii yɛn amim, na wonhyɛɛ yɛn so, na wonnyee obiara hɔ biribiara.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: AWURADE ne mo danseni, na deɛ wasra no yi ne ɔdanseni nnɛ, sɛ moanhunu biribiara me nsam. Na wɔkaa sɛ: Ɔne danseni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Ɛyɛ AWURADE a ɔyii Mose ne Aaron na ɔde mo agyanom firii Misraim asase so bae no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na afei mommɛgyina ha, na memmɔ mo soboɔ AWURADE anim, AWURADE teneneedeɛ a wayɛ ama mo ne mo agyanom nyinaa ho:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛberɛ a Yakob kɔɔ Misraim na Misraimfoɔ hyɛɛ wɔn soɔ no, mo agyanom su frɛɛ AWURADE, na AWURADE somaa Mose ne Aaron na wɔyii mo agyanom firii Misraim maa wɔbɛtenaa ha yi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nanso wɔn werɛ firii AWURADE wɔn Nyankopɔn, na ɔtɔn wɔn hyɛɛ Hasor sahene Sisera nsa ne Filistifoɔ nsa ne Moabhene nsa, na wɔne wɔn bɛkoe.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔsu frɛɛ AWURADE sɛ: Yɛayɛ bɔne sɛ yɛagya AWURADE hɔ akɔsom Baalim ne Astarot, na afei yi yɛn firi yɛn atamfoɔ nsam, na yɛbɛsom wo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na AWURADE somaa Yerubaal, Bedan, Yefta ne Samuel, na ɔyii mo firi mo atamfoɔ nsam hyia maa motenaa ase dwoodwoo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mohunuu sɛ Amonfoɔ hene Nahas reba mo soɔ no, moka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Dabi, na ɔhene mmɛdi yɛn so, berɛ a na AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn ne mo hene.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na afei, hwɛ, ɔhene a moyiiɛ a mosrɛɛ no no nie, na hwɛ, AWURADE asi mo so hene.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sɛ mosuro AWURADE na mosom no na motie no, na moante AWURADE anomu asɛm so atua na mo ne ɔhene a ɔdi mo soɔ no nyinaa redi AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn akyi a, anka ɛyɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na sɛ moantie AWURADE na mote AWURADE anomu asɛm so atua a, ɛnneɛ AWURADE nsa bɛda mo so sɛdeɛ ɛdaa mo agyanom soɔ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Afei nso mommɛgyina ha nhwɛ adeɛ kɛseɛ a AWURADE rebɛyɛ mo anim yi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnyɛ ayuotwa berɛ ne nnɛ? Mɛfrɛ AWURADE na wama aprannaa ne osuo aba, na moahwɛ ahunu sɛ mo bɔne a moayɛ AWURADE anim ne sɛ moabisa ɔhene afa no so.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna Samuel frɛɛ AWURADE, na AWURADE maa aprannaa ne osuo baa da no. Na ɔman no nyinaa suroo AWURADE ne Samuel sɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔman no nyinaa ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Bɔ AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn mpaeɛ ma wo nkoa, na yɛanwu, ɛfiri sɛ yɛde bɔne yi aka yɛn bɔne nyinaa ho, sɛ yɛabisa ɔhene afa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ: Monnsuro; moayɛ bɔne yi nyinaa deɛ, nanso AWURADE akyi na monnsane mmfire, na momfa mo akoma nyinaa nsom AWURADE.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na mommmane nnkɔdi ade hunu a mfasoɔ ne ɛgyeɛ nni ho no akyi, na ɛyɛ ade hunu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na AWURADE din kɛseɛ no nti ɔrempa ne man, na ɛsɔ AWURADE ani sɛ ɔde mo bɛyɛ ne man;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> me nso, ɛmpare me sɛ mɛgyae mo ho mpaebɔ de ayɛ AWURADE bɔne; na mɛkyerɛ mo kwan pa a ɛtene no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Suro nko na monsuro AWURADE, na momfa mo akoma nyinaa nsom no nokorɛ mu. Na monhwɛ adeɛ kɛseɛ a wayɛ ama mo no.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na sɛ bɔne ara na mobɛyɛ a, ɛnneɛ wɔbɛsesa mo ne mo hene nyinaa akɔ."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Saulo bɛdii hene na wadi bɛboro mfirinhyia aduasa. Na ɔdii Israel so hene mfeɛ mmienu no,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ɔyii Israel mu nnipa mpensa fae. Na wɔn mu mpennu wɔ Saulo nkyɛn, Mikmas ne Betel bepɔ so, na apem wɔ Yonatan nkyɛn Gibea-benyamin; na ɔman a aka no, ɔgyaa wɔn kwan maa wɔkɔɔ wɔn ntomadan mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yonatan kaa Filistifoɔ bansifoɔ a wɔwɔ Geba no gui; na Filistifoɔ teeɛ. Ɛnna Saulo hyɛnee totorobɛnto asase no nyinaa soɔ sɛ: Momma Hebrifoɔ nte!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Israel nyinaa tee sɛ Saulo aka Filistifoɔ bansifoɔ no agu, ɛne sɛdeɛ Israel ama wɔn ho ayɛ Filistifoɔ ahi. Na wɔhyiahyiaa ɔman no boaa ano, Saulo nkyɛn wɔ Gilgal.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Filistifoɔ boaboaa wɔn ano sɛ wɔne Israel rebɛko: Nteaseɛnam mpem aduasa ne apɔnkɔfoɔ mpemnsia ne dɔm a ne dodoɔ te sɛ mpoano anwea. Na wɔforo ba bɛkyeree nsraban Mikmas, Bet-awen apueeɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Israel mmarima no hunuu sɛ ɛredene wɔn, (ɛfiri sɛ wɔhyɛɛ ɔman no ahometeɛ), na ɔman no huntahuntaa abodan ne amena ne abotan ne aboda ne mmura mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Hebrifoɔ no bi twaa Yordan kɔɔ Gad ne Gilead asase so. Na Saulo da so wɔ Gilgal, na ɔman no nyinaa de ahopopoɔ dii n’akyi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔtwɛnee nnanson a ɛyɛ berɛ a Samuel hyɛeɛ no; nanso Samuel amma Gilgal, na ɔman no firii ne ho hwetee.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnna Saulo kaa sɛ: Momfa ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ no mmrɛ me. Na ɔbɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na hwɛ, ɔwiee ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no bɔ ara pɛ, na Samuel baeɛ; na Saulo firii adi sɛ ɔrekɔhyia no akyea no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna Samuel kaa sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na woayɛ yi? Na Saulo se: Mehunuu sɛ ɔman no refiri me ho ahwete, na wo nso woamma berɛ a wohyɛeɛ no, na Filistifoɔ aboa wɔn ano Mikmas,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ɛnna mese: Afei Filistifoɔ bɛsiane aba me so Gilgal, nso mennya menyii AWURADE mpaeɛ, enti na mehyɛɛ me ho mebɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Woadi nkwaseasɛm, woanni AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn mmara asɛm a ɔhyɛɛ woɔ no so. Na anka afei na AWURADE rebɛma w’ahennie atim Israel so daa:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na afei w’ahennie rennyina. AWURADE bɛhwehwɛ n’akoma so barima afa, na AWURADE asi ne man so hene, ɛfiri sɛ woanni deɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ woɔ no so.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Samuel sɔre firii Gilgal kɔɔ Gibea-benyamin. Na Saulo kan ɛdɔm a wɔne no wɔ hɔ no, mmarima bɛyɛ ahansia.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Saulo ne ne ba Yonatan ne ɛdɔm a wɔne wɔn wɔ hɔ no tenaa Gibea-benyamin, nso na Filistifoɔ akyere nsraban wɔ Mikmas.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na afomfafoɔ akuo mmiɛnsa firi Filistifoɔ nsram bae: Asafokuo baako te faa Ofra kwan so kɔɔ Sual asase so;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na asafokuo baako te faa Bet-horon kwan so, na asafokuo baako nso te faa ɛhyeɛ a ɛkyerɛ Seboim bonhwa no kwan so kɔɔ ɛserɛ so fam.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nanso na ɔtomfoɔ biara nni Israel asase no so baabiara, ɛfiri sɛ Filistifoɔ kaa sɛ: Anyɛ saa a, Hebrifoɔ bɛbɔ nkrantɛ ne mpea.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na na Israel nyinaa siane kɔ Filistifoɔ nkyɛn kɔse wɔn funtum nnadeɛ ne wɔn nsɔ ne wɔn nkuma ne wɔn kantankrankyi;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na wɔgye funtum nnadeɛ ne nsɔsɔ no biara ho dwetɛbena abupɛn mmiɛnsa mu baako, na wɔse nkuma anaa wɔsiesie nnadeɛ a wɔde ka mmoa nso a, wɔgye dwetɛbena abupɛn mmiɛnsa mu baako mmɔho.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na koda no, wɔanhunu nkrantɛ anaa pea ɛdɔm a wɔne Saulo ne Yonatan wɔ hɔ no mu biara nsam gye Saulo ne ne ba Yonatan nsam na wɔhunuu bie.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Filistifoɔ bansifoɔ no firii adi kɔɔ Mikmas tempɔn kwan so."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na da bi Saulo ba Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ n’abɔfra a ɔkura n’akodeɛ no sɛ: Bra ma yɛnkɔ Filistifoɔ bansifoɔ a wɔwɔ nohoa no ho. Nanso wanka ankyerɛ n’agya.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Saulo te Gibea kurotia, atoaa dua a ɛwɔ Migron no ase, na ɛdɔm a na wɔne no wɔ hɔ no bɛyɛ mmarima ahansia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Ahiya a ɔyɛ AWURADE sɔfoɔ Eli a ɔtenaa Silo no ba Pinehas ba Ikabod nua Ahitub ba hyɛ asɔfotadeɛ no. Na ɔman no nnim sɛ Yonatan kɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na tempɔn kwan a Yonatan pɛ sɛ ɔfa so kɔ Filistifoɔ bansifoɔ no soɔ no, ɔbotan a ano yɛ nnam wɔ ɔfa ha na ɔbotan a ano yɛ nnam nso wɔ ɔfa ha; baako din de Boses na baako din de Sene;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> baako ano kyerɛ atifi fam Mikmas ntentensoɔ, na baako ano kyerɛ anafoɔ fam Geba ntentensoɔ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ aberanteɛ a ɔkura n’akodeɛ no sɛ: Bra ma yɛntwam nkɔ momonotofoɔ bansifoɔ yi ho, ebia AWURADE bɛdi ama yɛn, na biribiara nsi AWURADE kwan sɛ ɔde ade bebree anaa ketewa bɛgye nkwa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na n’akodeɛkurani no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Yɛ deɛ ɛwɔ w’akomam nyinaa; dane wo ho, hwɛ, meka wo ho sɛdeɛ w’akoma pɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna Yonatan kaa sɛ: Hwɛ, yɛrebɛtwam akɔ nnipa no ho akɔyi yɛn ho akyerɛ wɔn,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na sɛ wɔka kyerɛ yɛn sɛ: Monnyina hɔ na yɛmmra mo nkyɛn a, ɛnneɛ yɛbɛgyina yɛn gyinabea na yɛremforo nkɔ wɔn nkyɛn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na sɛ wɔka sɛ: Momforo mmra yɛn so a, ɛnneɛ yɛbɛforo akɔ, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE de wɔn ahyɛ yɛn nsa, na yei bɛyɛ yɛn nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔn baanu no yiyii wɔn ho kyerɛɛ Filistifoɔ bansifoɔ no. Na Filistifoɔ no kaa sɛ: Hwɛ, Hebrifoɔ no refiri adi afiri ntokuro a wɔhuntahuntaa mu no mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na nsraban no mufoɔ buaa Yonatan ne n’akodeɛkurani no sɛ: Momforo mmra yɛn nkyɛn na yɛnkyerɛ mo biribi. Na Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ n’akodeɛkurani no sɛ: Foro di m’akyi, na AWURADE de wɔn ahyɛ Israel nsa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yonatan de ne nsa ne ne nan foroe, na n’akodeɛkurani no dii n’akyi, na wɔtotɔɔ Yonatan anim, na n’akodeɛkurani no kunkumm dii n’akyi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na nnipa a ɛdi kan a Yonatan ne n’akodeɛkurani kumm wɔn no bɛyɛ nnipa aduonu, wɔ mpasua a ɛbɛyɛ anantwie mpamho funtum kwan fa so.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ehu baa nsraban no mu, petee mu ne ɛdɔm no nyinaa mu; bansifoɔ no ne fomfafoɔ no nso ehu kaa wɔn, na asase no wosoe; na ɛyɛɛ ehu kɛse pa ara.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Saulo awɛmfoɔ a wɔwɔ Gibea-benyamin no hwɛe, na hwɛ, na nnipakuo no rehwete fa ha sene ha.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnna Saulo ka kyerɛɛ ɛdɔm a wɔne no wɔ hɔ no sɛ: Monkan na monhunu deɛ wafiri yɛn mu korɔ. Na wɔkanee, na hwɛ, na Yonatan ne n’akodeɛkurani nni hɔ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Ahiya sɛ: Kɔfa Nyankopɔn adaka no bra. Nso ɛda no na Nyankopɔn adaka no wɔ Israelfoɔ no nkyɛn.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Saulo ne ɔsɔfoɔ no rekasa no, Filistifoɔ nsram kitikitiyɛ no kɔɔ so dɔɔso ara. Ɛnna Saulo ka kyerɛɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no sɛ: Twe wo nsa!",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Saulo ne ɛdɔm a wɔka ne ho no nyinaa hyia boaa ano kɔɔ nsraban no mu, na hwɛ, na wɔn nyinaa de nkrantɛ reko tia wɔn ho, na ɛyɛ kitikiti kɛseɛ pa ara.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nso Hebrifoɔ a na wɔka Filistifoɔ no ho kane a wɔne wɔn foro baa nsraban no mu firi asase a atwa ahyia no soɔ no, wɔn nso bɛkaa Israelfoɔ a wɔka Saulo ne Yonatan ho no ho.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Israelfoɔ a wɔkɔhuntahuntaa Efraim bepɔ soɔ no nyinaa tee sɛ Filistifoɔ adwane no, wɔn nso tu saa wɔn ne wɔn koeɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛno nti AWURADE gyee Israel da no; na wɔkoeɛ ara kɔtwaa mu Bet-awen.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɛdenee Israel mmarima da no; na Saulo kaa ɔman no ntam sɛ: Nnome nka obiara a ɔbɛdidie ansa na onwunu adwoɔ, na mentɔ m’atamfoɔ so were. Enti ɔman no mu, obiara amfa aduane anka n’ano.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔman no nyinaa duruu kwaeɛ bi mu no, na ɛwoɔ wɔ fam.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔman no duruu kwaeɛ no mu no, na hwɛ, ɛwoɔ resosɔ; nanso obiara amfa ne nsa ankɔ n’ano, ɛfiri sɛ ɔman no suro ntam no.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Nso Yonatan deɛ, n’agya reka ɔman no ntam no, wante; na ɔde poma a na ɔkura no ano kaa ɛwoɔ no bi, na ɔde ne nsa kɔɔ n’ano, na n’ani so tetee no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na nkurɔfoɔ no mu baako kaa sɛ: W’agya aka dɔm no ntam sɛ: Nnome nka obiara a ɔbɛdidi nnɛ; nso na nkurɔfoɔ no retɔ piti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Yonatan kaa sɛ: M’agya aha asase yi. Monhwɛ sɛ mekaa ɛwoɔ yi kakra mehwɛeɛ yi, m’ani so atete me;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> na sɛ anka ɛdɔm yi dii wɔn atamfoɔ asadeɛ a wɔnyaeɛ no bi ɛ! Afei anka ɔkum kɛseɛ na Filistifoɔ kum no bɛyɛ.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na wɔkum Filistifoɔ no da no firi Mikmas kɔduruu Ayalon; na ɛdɔm no tɔɔ piti sɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ɛdɔm no to kɔhyɛɛ asadeɛ no so, na wɔfaa nnwan ne anantwie ne anantwie mma kunkumm wɔn ɛfam, na ɛdɔm no dii no mogya mu.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Hwɛ, ɛdɔm no reyɛ AWURADE bɔne sɛ wɔdi no mogya mu. Na ɔkaa sɛ: Moafom, mommuni ɔbo kɛseɛ mmrɛ me nnɛ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na Saulo kaa sɛ: Monhwete nkɔ ɛdɔm no mu nkɔka nkyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Momfa mo anantwie ne mo nnwan mmra me nkyɛn mmɛku wɔn ha nni, na monnyɛ AWURADE bɔne sɛ mobɛdi no mogya mu. Na ɛdɔm no nyinaa kurakura wɔn anantwie bae anadwo no bɛkunkum wɔn hɔ.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na Saulo sii afɔrebukyia maa AWURADE. Ɛno ne afɔrebukyia a ɛdi kan a ɔsi maa AWURADE.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na Saulo kaa sɛ: Momma yɛnsiane nkɔti Filistifoɔ no anadwo yi, na yɛmfom wɔn mfa nkɔduru anɔpa, na yɛannya wɔn mu nipa baako mpo. Na wɔkaa sɛ: Deɛ ɛyɛ wɔ w’ani soɔ nyinaa yɛ! Na ɔsɔfoɔ no kaa sɛ: Momma yɛntwe mpini Onyankopɔn wɔ ha.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na Saulo bisaa Onyankopɔn sɛ: Mensiane menti Filistifoɔ no anaa? Wode wɔn bɛhyɛ Israel nsa anaa? Na wammua no da no.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ɛnna Saulo kaa sɛ: Mo ɛdɔm mu atitire nyinaa, montwe mpini ha, na monhwɛ nhunu adekodeɛ a enti bɔne yi aba nnɛ.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE a ɔgye Israel te aseɛ yi, sɛ ɛwɔ me ba Yonatan mpo so a, wuo na ɔbɛwuo. Na ɛdɔm no mu biara ammua no.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ɛnna ɔka kyerɛɛ Israel nyinaa sɛ: Mo deɛ, monkɔ afa, na me ne me ba Yonatan nso nkɔ afa. Na ɛdɔm no ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Deɛ ɛyɛ wɔ w’ani soɔ no yɛ!",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na Saulo kaa sɛ: Ao, AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn, Adɛn nti na wommua w’akoa nnɛ yi? Sɛ ɛyɛ me anaa me ba Yonatan na ɛdi fɔ anaa Israelfoɔ yi a, ma nokorɛ nna adi. Na ɛbɔɔ Saulo ne ba Yonatan, na ɛdɔm no firii mu firii.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ɛnna Saulo kaa sɛ: Montwe me ne me ba Yonatan ntam ntonto. Na ɛbɔɔ Yonatan.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Yonatan sɛ: Kyerɛ me deɛ woyɛeɛ. Na Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ka na mede me nsam poma ti mekaa ɛwoɔ kakra mehwɛeɛ. Hwɛ, wuo na mɛwuo!",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na Saulo kaa sɛ: Yonatan, Onyankopɔn nyɛ saa na ɔnkɔ so nyɛ saa, sɛ wuo na wobɛwuo.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na ɛdɔm no ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Yonatan a wayɛ Israel mu ɔgyeɛ adwuma kɛseɛ yi nwu anaa? Ɛmpare no! Sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ yi, ne tirinwi baako mpo rentɔ fam, ɛfiri sɛ ɔne Onyankopɔn na ayɛ adeɛ nnɛ da yi. Na ɔman no gyee Yonatan na wanwu.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ɛnna Saulo firii Filistifoɔ no akyiridie sane baeɛ, na Filistifoɔ no kɔɔ wɔn nkuro mu.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Na Saulo dii Israel so hene no, ɔne n’atamfo nyinaa kɔko hyiae, ɔne Moab ne Amonfoɔ ne Edom ne Soba ahemfo ne Filistifoɔ koeɛ; na baabiara a ɔdanee ne ho koeɛ no, ɔdii nim.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ mmaninneɛ, na ɔkɔkumm Amalekfoɔ, na ɔgyee Israel wɔn afomfafoɔ nsam.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Nso Saulo mmammarima ne Yonatan, Isui ne Malkisua, na ne mmammaa baanu din nie: Abakan no din de Merab, na akumaa no din de Mikal.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Na Saulo yere din ne Ahinoam, Ahimaas ba. Na ne sahene din ne Abner, Saulo agya nua Ner ba.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Na Saulo agya Kis ne Abner agya Ner yɛ Abiel mma.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Na ɛko denden daa Filistifoɔ so Saulo nna nyinaa. Na sɛ Saulo hunu ɔbarima hoɔdenfoɔ biara anaa obiara a ɔyɛ nnam a, ɔkɔfa no ba ne nkyɛn."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Me na AWURADE somaa me sɛ memmɛsra wo ngo mensi wo ne man so hene: Na afei, tie AWURADE nsɛm.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Sɛɛ na asafo AWURADE seɛ: Mahunu deɛ Amalek yɛɛ Israel, sɛdeɛ wɔfiri Misraim reba no wɔbɛtwaree wɔn ɛkwan mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na afei kɔ na kɔkum Amalek, na monsɛe deɛ wɔwɔ nyinaa pasapasa, na nhu wɔn mmɔbɔ, na kum mmarima ne mmaa, mmɔfra ne nkɔkoaa, anantwie ne nnwan, yoma ne mfunumu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna Saulo maa ɔman no teeɛ, na ɔkan wɔn wɔ Telaim, mmarima a wɔnam anammɔn mu mpem ahanu ne Yuda mmarima mpem du.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Saulo duruu Amalek kuro kɛseɛ no so, na ɔde atɛfoɔ sisii bonhwa no mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Kenifoɔ no sɛ: Monkɔ, momfiri Amalek mu nsiane nkɔ, na mampra wo mamfra wɔn; na wo deɛ, woyɛɛ Israelfoɔ nyinaa adɔeɛ berɛ a wɔfiri Misraim reba no. Ɛnna Kenifoɔ firii Amalek mu kɔeɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Saulo kunkumm Amalek firii Hawila de kɔsii baabi a w’ani kyerɛ Sur a ɛda Misraim apueeɛ fam no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔkyeree Amalekhene Agag animono, na ɔman no nyinaa deɛ, ɔde nkrantɛ ano sɛee wɔn pasapasa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Saulo ne dɔm no hunuu Agag ne nnwan ne anantwie a wɔyɛ ne wɔn a wɔadodɔre sradeɛ ne nnwammuruwa ne deɛ ɛyɛ no nyinaa mmɔbɔ, na wɔampɛ sɛ wɔsɛe wɔn; na adeɛ biara a wɔmmuo na ɛnyɛ mma hwee no deɛ, wɔsɛee no pasapasa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE asɛm baa Samuel nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Manu me ho sɛ mede Saulo sii hene, ɛfiri sɛ wasane afiri m’akyi, na wamma me nsɛm annyina. Na ɛyɛɛ Samuel awerɛho, na ɔsu frɛɛ AWURADE anadwo no nyinaa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Samuel tuaa nhema sɛ ɔrekɔhyia Saulo anɔpa; na wɔka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Saulo aba Karmel, na hwɛ, wasi ne nkaeɛ dum, na wadane ne ho atwam asiane rekɔ Gilgal.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Samuel duruu Saulo nkyɛn no, Saulo ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: AWURADE nhyira wo. Mama AWURADE asɛm no atim.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Samuel kaa sɛ: Na ɛdeɛn ne nnwan su a ɛgu m’asom yi ne anantwie su a meteɛ yi?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Saulo se: Amalekfoɔ mu na wɔde firi baeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ ɔman no dodoo nnwan ne anantwie a ɛyɛ no ho sɛ wɔde rebɛbɔ afɔdeɛ ama AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn, na nkaeɛ no deɛ, yɛasɛe wɔn pasapasa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Gyae ma menka deɛ AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ me anadwo yi menkyerɛ wo. Na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Kasa ɛ!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Samuel kaa sɛ: Ɛwom sɛ woyɛ wo ara w’ani so ketewa deɛ, nanso ɛnyɛ wone Israel mmusuakuo ti? AWURADE sraa wo ngo sɛ di Israel so hene;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na AWURADE somaa wo akwankorɔ bi sɛ: Kɔ na kɔsɛe Amalekfoɔ nnebɔneyɛfoɔ no pasapasa, na ɛne wɔn nko kɔsi sɛ wobɛhye wɔn ase.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Adɛn nti na woantie AWURADE, na woato ahyɛ asadeɛ soɔ, na woayɛ deɛ ɛyɛ AWURADE ani so bɔne yi?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛnna Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Matie AWURADE, na makɔ kwan a AWURADE somaa me no, na mede Amalekhene Agag aba, na masɛe Amalek pasapasa!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔman no faa asadeɛ no mu nnwan ne anantwie, ahyiradeɛ no mu adikaneɛ, sɛ wɔde rebɛbɔ AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn afɔdeɛ Gilgal.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Samuel kaa sɛ: AWURADE pɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne okum afɔdeɛ sene tie a wobɛtie AWURADE anaa? Hwɛ, setie yɛ sene afɔdeɛ, na asoɔmmerɛ kyɛne nnwennini sradeɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na atuateɛ te sɛ woakɔ abisa, na asoɔden te sɛ amumuyɛ ne ahonisom. Ɛsiane sɛ woapo AWURADE asɛm nti, ɔno nso apo wo afiri ahennie no so.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛnna Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Mayɛ bɔne sɛ mafom wɔ AWURADE anomu asɛm ne wo nsɛm ho, sɛ mesuroo ɔman no na metiee wɔn.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na afei fa me bɔne firi me, na wo ne me nsane na menkɔsɔre AWURADE.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Me ne wo rensane nkɔ, ɛfiri sɛ woapo AWURADE asɛm, na AWURADE nso apo wo sɛ nni Israel so hene.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Samuel danee ne ho rekorɔ no, Saulo sɔɔ ne batakari ano, na ɛsuanee.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Suane na AWURADE asuane Israel ahennie afiri wo nsam nnɛ, na ɔde ama wo yɔnko a ɔyɛ sene woɔ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nso Israel Tumfoɔ no renni atorɔ na ɔrennu ne ho, ɛfiri sɛ ɔnyɛ onipa na wanu ne ho.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ɛnna ɔse: Mayɛ bɔne deɛ, nanso afei di me ni me man mpanimfoɔ ne Israel nyinaa anim: Ɛne me nsane nkɔ, na menkɔsɔre AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ɛnna Samuel sane kɔdii Saulo akyire; na Saulo kɔsɔree AWURADE.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na Samuel se: Momfa Amalekhene Agag mmrɛ me ha. Na Agag baa ne nkyɛn anigyeɛ so. Na Agag se: Ampa, owuoyea atwam kɔ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na Samuel se: Sɛ wo nkrantɛ maa mmaa dii mmasugya no, saa ara nso na wo na bɛdi basugya mmaa mu. Na Samuel twitwaa Agag AWURADE anim wɔ Gilgal.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ɛnna Samuel sii mu kɔɔ Rama. Na Saulo nso foro kɔɔ ne fie Gibea-saulo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na Samuel ammɛhwɛ Saulo bio kɔsii ne wuda, na Samuel gyam Saulo; na AWURADE nuu ne ho sɛ ɔde Saulo dii Israel so hene."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Wobɛgyam Saulo akɔsi da bɛn? Na me deɛ, mapo no sɛ ɔnnni Israel so hene. Fa ngo hyɛ w’abɛn ma, na bra ma mensoma wo Betlehemni Yisai nkyɛn, ɛfiri sɛ ne mma mu na mayi ɔhene mafa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Samuel se: Mɛyɛ dɛn makorɔ? Na Saulo te a, ɔbɛku me. Na AWURADE se: Fa nantwie ba kura na kɔka sɛ: Mebaa sɛ merebɛbɔ afɔdeɛ ama AWURADE.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na frɛ Yisai bra afɔdeɛ no ho, na me ara mɛkyerɛ wo deɛ yɛ, na sra deɛ mɛka makyerɛ woɔ no ma me.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Samuel yɛɛ sɛdeɛ AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ no no, na ɔkɔɔ Betlehem. Na kuro no mu mpanimfoɔ de ahopopoɔ bɛhyiaa no bisaa no sɛ: Woaba no asomdwoeɛ mu anaa?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔse: Asomdwoeɛ mu: Mebaa sɛ merebɛbɔ afɔdeɛ ama AWURADE; monnwira mo ho na mo ne me nkɔ afɔdeɛ no ho. Na ɔdwiraa Yisai ne ne mma no ho, na ɔfrɛɛ wɔn baa afɔdeɛ no ho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔbaa mu no, ɔhunuu Eliab, na ɔse: Ampa, deɛ AWURADE asra no no na ɔwɔ n’anim yi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Samuel sɛ: Nhwɛ ne ho tebea ne ne nipadua tenteneyɛ, na mempɛ no; na menhwɛ deɛ onipa hwɛ, na onipa hwɛ deɛ ɛtua aniwa, na AWURADE deɛ, ɔhwɛ akoma mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna Yisai frɛɛ Abinadab maa no twaa mu Samuel anim. Na ɔse: Oyi nso, AWURADE mfaa no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yisai maa Sama twaa mu. Na ɔse: Oyi nso, AWURADE mfaa no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Yisai maa ne mma baason bɛtwaa mu Samuel anim. Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Yisai sɛ: AWURADE nyii yeinom.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Samuel bisaa Yisai sɛ: Mmeranteɛ no nyinaa nie? Na ɔse: Aka akumaa no, na hwɛ, ɔrehwɛ nnwan. Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Yisai sɛ: Soma ma wɔnkɔfa no mmra, na yɛrentena ase gye sɛ waba ha ansa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔsoma maa wɔkɔfaa no baeɛ. Nso na ɔbere, na n’animma yɛ fɛ, na ne ho nso yɛ fɛ. Na AWURADE kaa sɛ: Sɔre sra no, na ɔno ara nie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ɛnna Samuel faa ngo abɛn no, na ɔsraa no ne nuanom mu. Na AWURADE honhom sii Dawid so, ɛfiri da no ara de rekorɔ no. Ɛnna Samuel sɔre baa Rama.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na AWURADE honhom firii Saulo ho, na honhommɔne firi AWURADE nkyɛn bɛhaa no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Saulo nkoa ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ ɛ, honhommɔne bi a ɛfiri Nyankopɔn nkyɛn na ɛreha woɔ yi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ma yɛn wura nka nkyerɛ wo nkoa a wɔwɔ w’anim yi, na wɔnkɔhwehwɛ obi a ɔnim sankuo bɔ, na sɛ honhommɔne no firi Nyankopɔn nkyɛn ba wo so a, ɔde ne nsa abɔ ama wo ho atɔ wo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ ne nkoa sɛ: Monhwehwɛ obi a ɔnim bɔ yie mma me ɛ, na momfa no mmrɛ me.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na mmeranteɛ no mu baako buaa sɛ: Hwɛ, mahunu Betlehemni Yisai ba bi a ɔnim bɔ, ɔyɛ ɔbarima a ɔtumi ne ho ne ɔkofoni, na ɔhunu nsɛm mu, na ne ho nso yɛ fɛ, na AWURADE di n’akyi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Saulo somaa abɔfoɔ maa wɔkɔɔ Yisai nkyɛn kɔkaa sɛ: Ma wo ba Dawid a ɔwɔ nnwan ho no mmra me nkyɛn.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Yisai faa afunumu de paanoo ne nsa kotokuo ma, ne ɔpapo soaa no, na ɔde somaa ne ba Dawid kɔmaa Saulo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Dawid baa Saulo nkyɛn, na ɔbɛyɛɛ ne somfoɔ. Na Saulo dɔɔ no sɛ, na ɔde no yɛɛ n’akodeɛkurani.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Saulo soma maa wɔkɔɔ Yisai nkyɛn kɔkaa sɛ: Mesrɛ wo, ma Dawid nsom me, na wanya m’anim adom.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ, sɛ honhom no firi Nyankopɔn nkyɛn ba Saulo so a, na Dawid afa sankuo na ɔde ne nsa abɔ, na Saulo ho adwo no, na ne ho atɔ no, na honhommɔne no afiri ne so kɔ."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Filistifoɔ boaboaa wɔn dɔm ano sɛ wɔrebɛdi ako, na wɔbɛboaa wɔn ano Soko a ɛyɛ Yuda dea no, na wɔbɛkyeree nsraban Soko ne Aseka ntam wɔ Efes-damim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Saulo ne Israel mmarima boaboaa wɔn ano na wɔkɔkyeree nsraban Ela bonhwa mu, na wɔtwitwaa mpasua sɛ wɔne Filistifoɔ rehyia akɔko.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Filistifoɔ gyina bepɔ so ɔfa ha, na Israel nso gyina bepɔ so ɔfa ha, na bonhwa da wɔn ntam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔbarima katakyie bi firi Filistifoɔ nsram firii adi, a ne din de Goliat a ɔfiri Gat, na ne tentene yɛ basafa mmiɛnsa ne saama.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na kɔbere mfrafraeɛ kyɛ hyɛ ne ti, na ɔhyɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ abono akotadeɛ, a n’akotadeɛ no mu duro yɛ nnwetɛbena mpemnum.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na kɔbere mfrafraeɛ nkataho kata ne nan ho, na kɔbere mfrafraeɛ pɛmɛ wɔ ne mmatiri so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ne pea dua te sɛ ntomanwomfoɔ nsadua, na ne pea ti kari dadeɛ nnwetɛbena ahansia; na ɛkyɛmkurani di n’anim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔbɛgyinaa hɔ teaa mu frɛɛ Israel mpasua ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Adɛn na moafiri aba mpasua so rebɛko yi? Menyɛ Filistini na mo nso moyɛ Saulo nkoa? Monyi mo mu ɔbarima bi, na ɔnsiane mmra me nkyɛn.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sɛ ɔtumi ne me ko na ɔku me a, ɛnneɛ yɛbɛyɛ mo nkoa; na sɛ me nso metumi no, na meku no a, ɛnneɛ monyɛ yɛn nkoa na monsom yɛn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Filistini no kaa sɛ: Me deɛ, meretwa Israel mpasua poa nnɛ da yi, momma me ɔbarima bi na yɛnko.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Saulo ne Israel nyinaa tee Filistini no nsɛm yi no, wɔn akoma tui, na wɔsuroo pa ara.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nso Dawid yɛ Efratini a ɔfiri Betlehem Yuda a wɔfrɛ no Yisai a ɔwɔ mmammarima baawɔtwe no ba. Na Saulo nna no mu na ɔbarima no abɔ akora a ne mfeɛ akɔ anim ara yie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yisai mma mpanin baasa dii Saulo akyi kɔɔ ɔsa no; na ne mma baasa a wɔkɔɔ ɔsa no din nie: Abakan Eliab ne n’akyiriba Abinadab ne deɛ ɔtɔ so mmiɛnsa Sama.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Dawid deɛ, na ɔno ne akumaa, na mpanimfoɔ baasa no dii Saulo akyiri kɔeɛ;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na Dawid deɛ, ɛyɛ a, ɔfiri Saulo nkyɛn sane kɔhwɛ n’agya nnwan wɔ Betlehem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na adaduanan, na Filistini no firi bɛgyina hɔ anɔpatutu ne anwummerɛ biara de ne ho kyerɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Yisai ka kyerɛɛ ne ba Dawid sɛ: Fa wo nuanom nnoɔma yi, nkyeweɛ efa yi ne paanoo du yi, tu mmirika kɔ nsraban no mu kɔma wo nuanom;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na fa nufosuo a akyenkyen mua du yi kɔma apem so safohene no, na hwɛ sɛdeɛ wo nuanom ho teɛ, na fa wɔn ho biribi bra.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nso na Saulo ne wɔn ne Israel mmarima nyinaa na ɛwɔ Ela bonhwa no mu ne Filistifoɔ reko.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Dawid sɔree anɔpahema gyaa nnwan no hyɛɛ ɔhwɛfoɔ nsa, na ɔsoa kɔeɛ, sɛdeɛ Yisai hyɛɛ no no; na ɔkɔduruu nteaseɛnam aboaeɛ; na ɛdɔm no refiri adi akɔ mpasua mu na wɔbɔɔ ɔko no ho se,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na Israel ne Filistifoɔ atwitwa mpasua a ɛdɔm kyerɛ dɔm anim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna Dawid gyaa ne nnoɔma a na ɔkura no hyɛɛ nnoɔma so hwɛfoɔ nsa, na ɔtuu mmirika kɔɔ mpasua no mu na ɔkɔkyeaa ne nuanom no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔne wɔn rekasa no, hwɛ, Filistini katakyie a wɔfrɛ no Goliat a ɔfiri Gat no, firi Filistifoɔ mpasua mu bae, na ɔbɛkekaa nsɛm no ara, na Dawid teeɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Israel mmarima no nyinaa, wɔhunu ɔbarima no a, wɔdwanedwane firi n’anim, na wɔsuro sɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Israel mmarima no kekaa sɛ: Sɛ moahunu ɔbarima a ɔreforo aba yi? Israel ara na waba rebɛtwa wɔn poa; na onii ko a ɔbɛku no no, ɔhene bɛma no anya ne ho sɛ, na ɔde ne babaa bɛma no aware, na wama n’agya fie ade wɔn ho wɔ Israel.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ mmarima a wɔne no gyina hɔ no sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na wɔbɛyɛ onipa a ɔbɛku Filistini yi na wayi ahohora afiri Israel soɔ no? Na hwan mpo ne Filistini momonoto yi a ɔtwa Onyankopɔn teasefoɔ mpasua poa yi?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na nkurɔfoɔ no kaa saa asɛm no ara kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sɛɛ na wɔbɛyɛ onipa a ɔbɛku no no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ne nua panin Eliab tee sɛ ɔne mmarima no rekasa; na Eliab bo fuu Dawid kaa sɛ: Adɛn nti na wosiane baa ha? Na hwan na wogyaa nnwan kakra a wɔwɔ wiram no hyɛɛ ne nsa? Me deɛ, menim w’aniɛden ne w’akoma mu bɔne dada sɛ ɔko no hwɛ nti na wosiane baeɛ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Dawid se: Na mayɛ dɛn? Ɛnyɛ asɛm bi ntira?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ɔdanee ne ho firii ne nkyɛn kyerɛɛ obi, na ɔkaa saa asɛm no ara; na nkurɔfoɔ no de akane asɛm no ara buaa no.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na wɔtee Dawid nsɛm a ɔkaeɛ no, wɔde kɔtoo Saulo anim, na ɔmaa wɔkɔfaa no baeɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Mma ne ho nnyɛ obiara akomatuo; w’akoa bɛkɔ akɔne Filistini yi ako.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Wontumi nkɔ nkɔne Filistini no nko, ɛfiri sɛ wo deɛ, woyɛ abɔfra, na ɔno deɛ, ɔyɛ ɔbarima kofoni firi ne mmɔfraase.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: W’akoa rehwɛ n’agya nnwan na sɛ gyata ne sisire ba bɛkyere adwammaa firi ekuo no mu a,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> mefiri adi meti no mekɔbɔ no, na meyi no mefiri n’anomu; na sɛ ɔsɔre tia me a, mesɔ ne bɔgyesɛ mu mebɔ no meku no.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> W’akoa akum gyata ne sisire nyinaa, na Filistini momonoto yi nyɛ sɛ wɔn mu baako, sɛ watwa Onyankopɔn teasefoɔ mpasua poa.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na Dawid kaa sɛ: AWURADE a ɔyii me gyata ne sisire nsam no, ɔno ara bɛyi me Filistini yi nsam. Ɛnna Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Kɔ, na AWURADE bɛdi w’akyi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na Saulo de ne ntadeɛ hyɛɛ Dawid na ɔde kɔbere mfrafraeɛ kyɛ soaa no, na ɔde nkataboɔ hyɛɛ no.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na Dawid de ne nkrantɛ bɔɔ n’atadeɛ no so, na ɔde nante hwɛe; ɛfiri sɛ na ɔnnya nsɔ nhwɛe. Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Merentumi mfa yeinom nkɔ, ɛfiri sɛ mensɔ menhwɛe da; na Dawid yi firii ne ho.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na ɔfaa ne poma kuraa ne nsam, na ɔyii mmoseaa a akokwa nnum firii subɔn no mu de guu ne nnwanhwɛfoɔ kotokuo ne bɔtɔ mu; na ɔkuraa ne ntɔmmoɔ ne nsam, na ɔtwe pinii Filistini no.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na Filistini no nso nam reba, na ɔtwe pinii Dawid; na ɔbarima a ɔso kyɛm no di n’anim.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na Filistini no totoo n’ani na ɔhunuu Dawid no, ɔbuu no animtia; ɛfiri sɛ ɔyɛ abɔfra, na ɔbere, na ne ho nso yɛ fɛ.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na Filistini no ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Meyɛ kraman na wode mpoma reba me nkyɛn yi? Na Filistini no frɛɛ ne nyame domee Dawid.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na Filistini no ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Bra me nkyɛn na memfa wo nam memma ewiem nnomaa ne wiram mmoa.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ɛnna Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Filistini no sɛ: Wo deɛ, wode nkrantɛ ne pea ne pɛmɛ na ɛreba me so, na me deɛ, mede asafo AWURADE, Israel mpasua a woatwa wɔn poa no Nyankopɔn din na mereba wo so.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ɛnnɛ da yi AWURADE de wo bɛhyɛ me nsa, na maku wo, na matwa wo tiri afiri so, na mede Filistifoɔ dɔm afunu mama ewiem nnomaa ne asase so mmoadoma nnɛ ara, na asase nyinaa ahunu sɛ Onyankopɔn bi wɔ Israel,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> na badwa yi nyinaa nso ahunu sɛ ɛnyɛ nkrantɛ ne pea na AWURADE de gye nkwa, ɛfiri sɛ ɔko no yɛ AWURADE dea, na ɔde mo bɛhyɛ yɛn nsa.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ, Filistini no sɔree sɛ ɔreba abɛhyia Dawid no, Dawid yɛɛ ntɛm tuu mmirika kɔɔ mpasua no so kɔhyiaa Filistini no.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Na Dawid tenee ne nsa hyɛɛ kotokuo no mu yii ɔboɔ wɔ mu, na ɔtoo ntɔmmoɔ no bɔɔ Filistini no moma so, na ɔboɔ no hyɛnee ne tirim, na ɔhwee ase maa n’anim butuu fam.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Saa na Dawid de ntɔmmoɔ ne ɔboɔ faa Filistini no soɔ, na ɔbɔɔ Filistini no kumm no, nanso na nkrantɛ biara nkura Dawid nsam.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Enti Dawid tutuu mmirika kɔgyinaa Filistini no so, na ɔsɔɔ ne nkrantɛ mu twe firii bɔha mu, na ɔkumm no, na ɔde twaa ne ti. Na Filistifoɔ no hunuu sɛ wɔn brane awuo no, wɔdwaneeɛ.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Ɛnna Israel ne Yuda mmarima sɔre bɔɔ ose na wɔtii Filistifoɔ no kɔduruu Gai ne Ekron apono akyi. Na Filistifoɔ apirafoɔ no totɔɔ Saaraim kwan so de kɔduruu Gat ne Ekron.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no sane firii Filistifoɔ no akyiridie ne pamo denden no mu, na wɔbɛfomm wɔn nsraban no faeɛ.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Na Dawid faa Filistini no ti, na ɔde baa Yerusalem; na n’akodeɛ deɛ, ɔde guu ne ntomadan mu.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Na Saulo hunuu Dawid sɛ ɔrefiri adi akɔhyia Filistini no no, ɔka kyerɛɛ ne safohene Abner sɛ: Abner, hwan ba ne aberanteɛ yi? Na Abner se: Ɔhene, sɛ wo kra te aseɛ yi, mennim.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Na ɔhene se: Wo deɛ, bisa onii ko a ne ba ne akwankwaa yi.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Na Dawid firi Filistini no kum resane aba no, Abner faa no de no baa Saulo anim, na Filistini no tiri no kura ne nsam.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Aberanteɛ, hwan ba ne wo? Na Dawid buaa sɛ: W’akoa Yisai, Betlehemni no ba ne me."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔne Saulo kasa wieeɛ no, na Yonatan kra akyekyere Dawid kra ho, na Yonatan dɔɔ no sɛ ɔno ara ne kra.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛda no ara, Saulo faa no ne no tenaeɛ, na wamma no ansane ankɔ n’agya fie.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yonatan ne Dawid pam apam bi, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔdɔ no sɛ ɔno ara ne kra.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Yonatan yii ne batakari a ɔhyɛ no maa Dawid ne ne ntadeɛ kɔduruu ne nkrantɛ ne ne tadua ne n’abɔsoɔ so.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Dawid firi adi kɔ baabiara a Saulo soma no na ne biribiara kɔ so; na Saulo de no sii akofoɔ so, na ɔsɔɔ ɔman no nyinaa ne Saulo nkoa nso ani.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔreba a Dawid resane afiri Filistini no kum aba no, mmaa firii Israel nkuro nyinaa mu de nnwom ne asa ba bɛhyiaa Ɔhene Saulo; wɔde mpintin ne anigyeɛ ne ahinasa adeɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mmaa a wɔregorɔ no gyee wɔn ho so sɛ: Saulo akum apem mu, na Dawid akum ne mpem du mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Saulo bo fuu kɛse, na asɛm no anyɛ no dɛ. Na ɔkaa sɛ: Wɔde mpem du ama Dawid, na me deɛ, apem na wɔde ama me, na ɛdeɛn na aka no bio sɛ ahennie no?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɛfiri da no ara de rekorɔ no, Saulo tuu n’ani saa Dawid.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, Nyankopɔn honhommɔne no sii Saulo so, na ɔrekɔm efie, na Dawid de ne nsa rebɔ sankuo, sɛdeɛ ɔyɛ daa no; na pea kura Saulo nsam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Saulo too pea no, na ɔse: Mɛbɔ Dawid afam ɔfasuo ho. Na Dawid danee ne ho firii n’anim mprenu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Saulo suroo Dawid, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE di n’akyi, na Saulo deɛ, wafiri ne nkyɛn.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Enti Saulo yii no firii ne ho, na ɔsii no apem so safohene, na ɔdii ahyɛmfire, ɔman no anim.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Dawid nyaa nkɔsoɔ n’akwan nyinaa mu, na AWURADE dii n’akyi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Saulo hunuu sɛ ne biribiara kɔ soɔ no, ɔsuroo no kɔkɔɔkɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Israel ne Yuda nyinaa dɔɔ Dawid, ɛfiri sɛ ɔno na na ɔdi wɔn anim ahyɛmfire.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Hwɛ, me babaa panin Merab nie, ɔno na mede no bɛma wo aware; nnam ara na yɛ ma me, na ko ma AWURADE! Ɛfiri sɛ Saulo dwenee sɛ: Meremma me nsa nnka no, na Filistifoɔ na wɔn nsa nka no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Mene hwan, na me nkwa, anaa m’agya abusua ne deɛn wɔ Israel, na memmɛyɛ ɔhene aseɛ?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na berɛ duruiɛ a anka wɔde Saulo babaa Merab rebɛma Dawid no, wɔde no maa Meholatni Adriel awareɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Saulo ba Mikal dɔ Dawid; na wɔka kyerɛɛ Saulo no, asɛm no yɛɛ no anigyeɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Saulo se: Mede no bɛma no, na ayɛ no fidie, na Filistifoɔ nsa aka no. Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Dawid ne mprenu soɔ sɛ: Wobɛyɛ m’ase nnɛ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Saulo hyɛɛ n’asomfoɔ sɛ: Momfa aseɛ ne Dawid nkasa sɛ: Hwɛ, ɔhene pɛ w’asɛm, na ne nkoa nyinaa dɔ wo, enti afei, bɛyɛ ɔhene ase.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Saulo nkoa no kaa nsɛm yi guu Dawid aso mu. Na Dawid kaa sɛ: Ɛyɛ mo ani so adewa sɛ obi bɛyɛ ɔhene aseɛ? Na me deɛ, meyɛ onipa hiani a m’akyiri nyɛ duro.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Saulo nkoa kɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sɛdeɛ Dawid kaeɛ nie.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Saulo kaa sɛ: Sɛ monkɔka nkyerɛ Dawid nie: Ɔhene mpɛ tiriadeɛ biara sɛ Filistifoɔ mmarima ano wedeɛ ɔha, na wɔntɔ ɔhene atamfoɔ so were. Na Saulo susuu sɛ ɔnam Filistifoɔ nsa so bɛma Dawid atɔ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ne nkoa kɔkaa nsɛm yi kyerɛɛ Dawid no, ɛyɛɛ Dawid fɛ sɛ ɔbɛyɛ ɔhene aseɛ. Na nna no nnya nnuruiɛ no,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Dawid sɔre sii mu, ɔno ne ne mmarima, na ɔkɔkumm Filistifoɔ mmarima ahanu. Na Dawid de wɔn mmarima ano wedeɛ baeɛ, na wɔkan maa no durui de kyerɛɛ ɔhene sɛ, ɔnyɛ ɔhene ase. Na Saulo de ne ba Mikal maa no aware.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Saulo hwɛ hunuu sɛ AWURADE di Dawid akyi; na Saulo babaa Mikal dɔɔ no.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Saulo kɔɔ so suroo Dawid ara, na ɛmaa Saulo tanee Dawid daa.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Filistifoɔ asafohene firii adi bɛkoeɛ; na da biara a wɔfiri adi ba no, ɛsi Dawid yie sene Saulo nkoa nyinaa. Na na wɔbɔ ne din anidie mu sɛ."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ ne ba Yonatan ne ne nkoa nyinaa sɛ wɔnkum Dawid.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nanso Saulo ba Yonatan pɛ Dawid asɛm sɛ. Na Yonatan kɔka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: M’agya Saulo rehwehwɛ wo aku wo, na afei, kora wo ho anɔpa, na tena kokoa bi mu hunta;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na me deɛ, mɛfiri adi makɔgyina m’agya nkyɛn wiram baabi a wowɔ no, na me ne m’agya aka wo ho asɛm, na mete biribi a maka makyerɛ wo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Yonatan kaa Dawid ho asɛmpa kyerɛɛ n’agya Saulo, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Mma ɔhene nnyɛ n’akoa Dawid ho bɔne; na ɔnyɛɛ wo bɔne biara, na ne nneyɛɛ nso ayɛ wo yie pii.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔde ne kra too ne nsam kɔkumm Filistini no, na AWURADE dii nkonim kɛse maa Israel nyinaa. Wohunui na w’ani gyeeɛ; na adɛn nti na worebɛyɛ mogya a ɛdi bem ho bɔne na woakum Dawid kwa?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Saulo tiee Yonatan, na Saulo kaa ntam sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ yi, wɔrenkum no da!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Yonatan frɛɛ Dawid; na Yonatan kaa nsɛm no nyinaa kyerɛɛ no. Ɛnna Yonatan de Dawid baa Saulo nkyɛn, na ɔbɛtenaa n’anim sɛ kane no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔko no kɔɔ so ara, na Dawid firii adi ne Filistifoɔ kɔkoeɛ, na ɔde ekumkɛseɛ kumm wɔn, na wɔdwane firii n’anim.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na AWURADE honhommɔne no baa Saulo so; na ɔte ne fie, na pea kura ne nsam, na Dawid de ne nsa rebɔ sankuo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Saulo hwehwɛɛ sɛ ɔde pea no bɔ Dawid fam ɔfasuo no ho, nanso ɔtwee ne ho firii Saulo anim, na ɔtoo pea no wɔɔ ɔfasuo no mu; na Dawid dwaneeɛ, na ɔfirii mu firii anadwo no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna Saulo somaa abɔfoɔ kɔɔ Dawid fie sɛ wɔnkɔwɛn no na wɔnku no anɔpa. Na Dawid yere Mikal ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sɛ woannye wo kra anadwo yi a, ɔkyena wɔbɛku wo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Mikal de Dawid faa mpomma mu sii fam, na ɔkɔeɛ, na ɔdwane firii mu firii.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Mikal faa ohoni de too mpa no so, na ɔde abirekyie nwi sumiiɛ too atifi, na ɔde ntoma kataa so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Saulo somaa abɔfoɔ sɛ wɔnkɔfa Dawid no, Mikal kaa sɛ: Ɔyare.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ɛnna Saulo somaa abɔfoɔ no sɛ wɔnkɔhwɛ Dawid, na ɔse: Momfa no mfiri mpa no so mmrɛ me, na menku no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na abɔfoɔ no duruu hɔ no, na hwɛ, ohoni na ɛda mpa no soɔ, na abirekyie nwi sumiiɛ da atifi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Mikal sɛ: Adɛn nti na woadaadaa me sɛɛ, na woagya me tamfo kwan na wafiri mu afire yi? Na Mikal ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Ɔno na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Ma menkɔ; adɛn nti na menku woɔ?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Dawid dwane firii mu firiiɛ, na ɔkɔɔ Samuel nkyɛn Rama kɔkaa deɛ Saulo de ayɛ no nyinaa kyerɛɛ no. Na ɔne Samuel kɔ kɔtenaa Naiot.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Hwɛ, Dawid wɔ Naiot wɔ Rama.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Saulo somaa abɔfoɔ sɛ wɔnkɔfa Dawid; na wɔhunuu adiyifoɔ asafo no sɛ wɔrehyɛ nkɔm na Samuel gyina hɔ rehwɛ wɔn soɔ no, Nyankopɔn honhom baa Saulo abɔfoɔ no so, na wɔn nso hyehyɛɛ nkɔm.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔbɛka kyerɛɛ Saulo no, ɔsomaa abɔfoɔ foforɔ; na wɔn nso hyehyɛɛ nkɔm saa ara. Na Saulo somaa abɔfoɔ bio, ne mprɛnsa so, na wɔn nso hyehyɛɛ nkɔm.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna ɔno ara kɔɔ Rama, na ɔduruu abura kɛseɛ a ɛwɔ Seku ho no, ɔbisaa sɛ: Ɛhe na Samuel ne Dawid wɔ? Na wɔse: Hwɛ, wɔwɔ Naiot wɔ Rama.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔkɔɔ Naiot wɔ Rama hɔ; na Nyankopɔn honhom baa ɔno nso so, na ɔrekorɔ no, ɔhyɛɛ nkɔm ara kɔ kɔsii sɛ ɔduruu Naiot wɔ Rama.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔno nso worɔɔ ne ntadeɛ, na ɔno nso hyɛɛ nkɔm Samuel anim, na ɔde adagya daa hɔ da mu no nyinaa ne anadwo mu no nyinaa. Enti na wɔka sɛ: Saulo nso fra adiyifoɔ no mu anaa?"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Dawid dwane firii Naiot wɔ Rama, na ɔba bɛkaa no Yonatan anim sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na mayɛ? M’amumuyɛ ne sɛn, na me bɔne ne sɛn wɔ w’agya anim a enti ɔrehwehwɛ me aku me yi?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ɛmpare wo, worenwu; hwɛ, m’agya renyɛ ade kɛseɛ anaa ade ketewa biara gye sɛ ɔyi me asotire ansa; na adɛn nti na m’agya de asɛm yi bɛhunta me? Ɛnte saa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Dawid kaa ntam nso sɛ: W’agya nim sɛ manya w’anim adom, enti na ɔse: Wɔmmma Yonatan nnhunu yei, na anyɛ no ya; na ampa ara, sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ, na wo kra nso te aseɛ yi, nammɔn pɛ na ɛda me ne owuo ntam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Biribiara a wo kra seɛ no, mɛyɛ ama wo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Yonatan sɛ: Hwɛ, ɔkyena na ɔsrane fire a ɛsɛ sɛ anka me ne ɔhene kɔtena adidiiɛ; nanso ma menkɔ nkɔhunta wiram nkɔsi da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no anwummerɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sɛ w’agya bisa m’akyiri kwan a, ɛnneɛ ka kyerɛ no sɛ: Dawid asrɛ me kwan sɛ ɔretu mmirika akɔ ne kurom Betlehem, na abusua no nyinaa wɔ afirinhyia afɔrebɔ wɔ hɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sɛ ɔka sɛ: Ɛyɛ a, na asomdwoeɛ wɔ hɔ ma w’akoa, na sɛ ne bo fu a, ɛnneɛ hunu sɛ wakyere ne mu sa bɔne.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na yɛ w’akoa adɔeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE apam mu na woama wo ne w’akoa ahyɛne; na sɛ amumuyɛ bi wɔ me mu a, wo ara ku me, na adɛn nti na wode me rekɔma w’agya?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yonatan se: Ɛmpare wo sɛ, sɛ menim sɛ m’agya akyere sa bɔne de reba wo so a, merenka menkyerɛ woɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Yonatan sɛ: Sɛ w’agya de asɛm denden bi bua wo a, hwan na ɔbɛka akyerɛ me?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Bra ma yɛmfiri nkɔ wiram. Na wɔn baanu firii adi kɔɔ wiram.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn, nyɛ danseni sɛ, sɛ ɔkyena anaa ɔkyena akyi sɛsɛɛ berɛ yi mu, mehwɛ m’agya adwene na ɛyɛ wɔ Dawid ho, na mansoma amma wo nkyɛn ammɛyi wo asotire a!",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na sɛ ɛsɔ m’agya ani sɛ bɔne mmra wo so na mamma ammɛyi wo asotire, na mannya wo kwan amma woankɔ asomdwoeɛ mu a, AWURADE nyɛ me Yonatan saa na ɔnka ho saa! Na AWURADE nni w’akyi sɛdeɛ ɔdi m’agya akyire no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na sɛ meda so mete aseɛ yi, fa AWURADE nokorɛ adɔeɛ yɛ me, na manwu,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ntwa w’adɔeɛ no to mfiri me fie ho da. Na sɛ AWURADE twitwa Dawid atamfoɔ firi asase so a, nnyae me fie adɔeɛyɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Yonatan ne Dawid fie pamee sɛ: AWURADE ntɔ Dawid atamfoɔ were.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Yonatan maa Dawid kaa ne dɔ a ɔde dɔ no no ho ntam bio, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔdɔ no sɛ ɔno ara ne kra.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ɔkyena na ɔsrane fire, na wɔbɛhunu sɛ wonni hɔ, ɛfiri sɛ wo tenaberɛ bɛda mpan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na sɛ ɛdi nnansa a, wɔbɛhunu sɛ wonni hɔ ampa ara, ɛnneɛ na siane ntɛm bra deɛ asɛm no baeɛ no, wohuntaeɛ hɔ, na tena Esel boɔ no ho.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na mɛtoto agyan mmiɛnsa mafa ho, sɛdeɛ merebɔ botaeɛ mu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na hwɛ, mɛsoma abɔfra sɛ: Kɔhwehwɛ agyan no. Sɛ mese abɔfra no sɛ: Hwɛ, agyan no wɔ wo nkyɛn mu ha, tase bra a, ɛnneɛ bra, na sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ yi, asomdwoeɛ na ɛwɔ hɔ ma woɔ, asɛm biara nni hɔ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na sɛ mese akwankwaa no sɛ: Hwɛ, m’agyan no wɔ w’anim fam nohoa a, ɛnneɛ kɔ, na AWURADE agya wo kwan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na asɛm a me ne wo kaeɛ no ho deɛ, hwɛ, AWURADE wɔ me ne wo ntam daa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛnna Dawid kɔhuntaa wiram. Na ɔsrane firiiɛ no, ɔhene kɔtenaa adidiiɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔhene tenaa n’atenaeɛ sɛdeɛ ɔyɛ no daa wɔ ɔfasuo ho adwa no so; na Yonatan sɔree, na Abner tenaa ɔhene nkyɛn, na Dawid atenaeɛ no da mpan.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Saulo anka hwee da no; ɛfiri sɛ ɔse: Biribi ayɛ no; ne ho nte; ampa ara ne ho nte.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ a ɛyɛ bosome no da a ɛtɔ so mmienu a na Dawid atenaeɛ da mpan no, Saulo bisaa ne ba Yonatan sɛ: Adɛn nti na Yisai ba no amma adidie ase nnora ne nnɛ yi?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Yonatan buaa Saulo sɛ: Dawid srɛɛ me kwan sɛ ɔrekɔ Betlehem,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> na ɔse: Gya me kwan ɛ, na yɛwɔ abusua afɔrebɔ wɔ kuro no mu, na me nua ahyɛ me sɛ memmra. Enti afei, sɛ manya w’anim adom a, ma menkɔ menkɔhwɛ me nuanom. Enti na wamma ɔhene pono ho yi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ɛnna Saulo bo fuu Yonatan, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Wo, ɔbaa brakyewni tuateni ba, adɛn menhunuu sɛ woafa Yisai ba no adamfo de rehyɛ wo ho ne wo na adagya mu aniwuo?",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na mmerɛ dodoɔ a Yisai ba no te ase asase soɔ yi, wo ne w’ahennie rennyina. Enti soma ma wɔnkɔfa no mmrɛ me, na wuo ara na ɔbɛwuo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na Yonatan buaa n’agya Saulo ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Adɛn nti na wɔnku no? Ɛdeɛn na wayɛ?",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ɛnna Saulo too pea sɛ ɔde rebɔ no. Na Yonatan hunuu sɛ n’agya awe ataa so sɛ ɔbɛkum Dawid.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na Yonatan de abufuhyeɛ sɔre firii ɛpono no ho, na wannidi bosome no da a ɛtɔ so mmienu no. Na ɔdii Dawid ho ya sɛ n’agya asopa no.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na anɔpa no Yonatan firii adi kɔɔ wiram deɛ ɔhyɛɛ Dawid no, na abɔfra kumaa bi ka ne ho.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ n’abɔfra no sɛ: Tu mmirika kɔhwehwɛ agyan a merebɛtotoɔ no. Abɔfra no retu mmirika no, ɔtoo agyan no traa no.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na abɔfra no duruu deɛ agyan a Yonatan toeɛ no wɔ no, Yonatan hyɛɛ abɔfra no mmɔn sɛ: Agyan no ngu w’anim nohoa anaa?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na Yonatan hyɛɛ abɔfra no mmɔn sɛ: Yɛ ntɛm, ka wo ho, nnyina. Na Yonatan abɔfra no tasee agyan no de brɛɛ ne wura.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Nso na abɔfra no nnim ho hwee; Yonatan ne Dawid nko ara na na wɔnim asɛm no.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ɛnna Yonatan de n’akodeɛ no maa abɔfra no na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Fa kɔ kuro no mu.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Abɔfra no kɔeɛ; na Dawid sɔre firii aboɔkuo no ho, na ɔde n’anim bɛbutuu fam na ɔkotoo mprɛnsa, na wɔfefee wɔn ano, na wɔn baanu sui ara maa Dawid deɛ boroo so.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na Yonatan ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Kɔ asomdwoeɛ mu. Sɛdeɛ yɛn baanu akeka AWURADE ntam no, AWURADE ntena me ne wo ntam ne m’asefoɔ ne w’asefoɔ ntam nkɔsi daa. Na ɔsii mu kɔeɛ; na Yonatan baa kuro no mu."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Dawid baa Nob Ɔsɔfoɔ Ahimelek nkyɛn. Na Ahimelek de ahopopoɔ bɛhyiaa Dawid, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Adɛn nti na wo nko ara wonam na onipa biara nka wo ho yi?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Ɔsɔfoɔ Ahimelek sɛ: Ɔhene ahyɛ me asɛm bi die, na waka akyerɛ me sɛ: Mma obiara nnhunu adekodeɛ a meresoma wo ho ne deɛ mahyɛ woɔ no ho biribiara; na mmeranteɛ no nso, mahyɛ wɔn sɛ wɔnkɔ baabi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na afei, ɛdeɛn na ɛwɔ wo nsam? Ma me paanoo nnum anaa biribiara a wobɛnya.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no buaa Dawid sɛ: Paanoo hunu biara nni me nsam, sɛ paanoo kronkron na ɛwɔ hɔ; sɛ mmeranteɛ no akora wɔn ho afiri mmaa ho nko a!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Dawid buaa see ɔsɔfoɔ no sɛ: Ampa, wɔmma mmaa mmɛn yɛn berɛ biara a yɛrekɔ akɔdi dwuma bi no; na mmeranteɛ no adeɛ ho te, na nkantom nnɛ a ɛsɛ sɛ wɔn adeɛ ho teɛ yi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna ɔsɔfoɔ no de akronkronneɛ no maa no, ɛfiri sɛ na paanoo biara nni hɔ sɛ Kyerɛ paanoo a wɔyi firi AWURADE anim de paanoohyeɛ bɛgu hɔ da a wɔyiiɛ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nso na Saulo nkoa mu nipa bi wɔ hɔ da no, a wɔato no mu AWURADE anim, ne din de Doeg, Edomni a ɔyɛ Saulo mmoahwɛfoɔ mu panin.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Ahimelek sɛ: Pea anaa nkrantɛ biara nni wo nsam ha? Na me nkrantɛ ne me nnoɔma mpo mamfa mankura, ɛfiri sɛ ɔhene asɛm no, wɔpɛ no ntɛm.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no kaa sɛ: Filistini Goliat a wokum no Ela bonhwa mu no nkrantɛ, hwɛ, ɛno na wɔabobɔ no ntoma mu da asɔfotadeɛ no akyire no, ɛno na wobɛfa a, fa, na foforɔ biara nni ha sɛ ɛno. Na Dawid kaa sɛ: Ebi nte sɛ ɛno, fa ma me!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Dawid sɔre dwanee da no Saulo anim, na ɔkɔɔ Gathene Akis nkyɛn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Akis nkoa ka kyerɛɛ ɔhene sɛ: Ɛnyɛ Dawid, asase no so hene no nie? Ɛnyɛ oyi na wɔtoo ne ho dwom asa mu kaa sɛ: Saulo akum n’apem, na Dawid akum ne mpem du no?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Dawid de nsɛm yi siee n’akoma mu, na ɔsuroo Gat hene Akis anim sɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔsakyeraa ne suban wɔn anim, na ɔboapa yɛɛ ne ho bɔdamfoɔ wɔn nsam, na ɔwerɛwerɛɛ kuro no apono nta ho, na ɔmaa ne ntasuo sinsianee n’abɔgyesɛ mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛnna Akis ka kyerɛɛ ne nkoa sɛ: Hwɛ, mohunu sɛ onipa yi abɔ dam, na adɛn nti na mode no abrɛ me?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Abɔdamfoɔ abɔ me na mode oyi aba sɛ ɔmmɛdi me so abɔdansɛm yi? Oyi mmra me fie anaa?"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Dawid firi hɔ kɔeɛ, na ɔdwane kɔɔ Adulam bodan mu. Na ne nuanom ne n’agya fie nyinaa teeɛ no, wɔsiane kɔɔ ne nkyɛn hɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔn a wɔn ho akyere wɔn ne wɔn a wɔdede aka ne wɔn a wɔn werɛ ahoɔ boaboaa wɔn ano baa ne nkyɛn, na ɔdii wɔn so safohene. Mmarima bɛyɛ ahanan na wɔbɛkaa ne ho.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Dawid firii hɔ kɔɔ Mispe wɔ Moab, na ɔka kyerɛɛ Moabhene sɛ: Mesrɛ wo, ma m’agya ne me na mmɛtena mo nkyɛn nkɔsi sɛ mɛhunu deɛ Onyankopɔn bɛyɛ me ansa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔgyaa wɔn Moabhene no nkyɛn, na wɔtenaa ne nkyɛn nna a Dawid wɔ bepɔ so atenaeɛ hɔ nyinaa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Odiyifoɔ Gad ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Ntena bepɔ so atenaeɛ hɔ, na sim kɔ Yuda asase so. Na Dawid sii mu baa Heret kwaeɛ mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Saulo tee sɛ wɔahunu deɛ Dawid ne nnipa a wɔka ne ho no wɔ. Na Saulo te Gibea, santɛ dua bi ase wɔ kokoɔ so, na ne pea kura ne nsam, na ne nkoa nyinaa gyinagyina ne ho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ n’asomfoɔ a wɔgyinagyina ne ho no sɛ: Mo Benyaminfoɔ, montie! Yisai ba no nso bɛmema mo nyinaa mfuo ne bobe nturo na ɔde mo nyinaa asisi mpempem so asafohene ne ɔha ha so asafohene?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sɛɛ mo nyinaa moapam me tiri so, na obiara nni hɔ a oyi me asotire, sɛ me ba ne Yisai ba no apam, na mo mu biara nni hɔ a ɔdi me ho ya na ɔyi me asotire sɛ me ba de m’akoa agyina hɔ ne me redi asie, sɛ ɔntɛ me sɛdeɛ ɛte nnɛ yi?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnna Edomni Doeg a ɔno nso gyina Saulo nkoa no nkyɛn no buaa sɛ: Mehunuu Yisai ba no sɛ ɔbaa Nob, Ahitub ba Ahimelek nkyɛn",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na ɔbisaa AWURADE maa no, na ɔmaa no akwansoduane, na ɔde Filistini Goliat nkrantɛ no maa no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna ɔhene soma maa wɔkɔhyiaa Ahitub ba Ɔsɔfoɔ Ahimelek ne n’agya fie asɔfoɔ a wɔwɔ Nob no nyinaa, na wɔn nyinaa baa ɔhene nkyɛn.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Saulo kaa sɛ: Ahitub ba, tie ɛ! Na ɔbuaa sɛ: Menie, me wura.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Adɛn nti na wo ne Yisai ba no apam me tiri soɔ, na womaa no aduane ne nkrantɛ, na wobisaa Onyankopɔn maa no, sɛ ɔnsɔre me so na ɔntetɛ me sɛdeɛ ɛte nnɛ yi?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Ahimelek buaa ɔhene sɛ: Na wo nkoa nyinaa mu hwan na ɔyɛ ɔnokwafoɔ sɛ Dawid a ɔyɛ ɔhene ase, na ɔtie w’asɛm, na wɔdi no ni wɔ wo fie?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nnɛ na merefiri aseɛ mabisa Onyankopɔn mama no anaa? Yei mpare me! Mma ɔhene mmfa asɛm bi nnto n’akoa anaa m’agya fie nyinaa so, na w’akoa nnim yeinom nyinaa ho hwee, ketewa oo, kɛseɛ oo!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔhene kaa sɛ: Ahimelek, wuo ara na wobɛwuo, wo ne w’agya fie nyinaa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔhene ka kyerɛɛ awɛmfoɔ a wɔgyinagyina ne ho no sɛ: Monnanedane mo ho nkum AWURADE asɔfoɔ no, na wɔn nsa nso wɔ Dawid deɛ mu, na wɔnim sɛ ɔredwane, na wɔanyi me asotire. Na ɔhene nkoa no ampɛ sɛ wɔtene wɔn nsa ka AWURADE asɔfoɔ no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna ɔhene ka kyerɛɛ Doeg sɛ: Wo deɛ, dane wo ho na ka asɔfoɔ no. Na Edomni Doeg danee ne ho na ɔkaa asɔfoɔ no kumm mmarima aduɔwɔtwe nnum a wɔhyɛ nwera asɔfotadeɛ da no ara.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na asɔfoɔ kuro Nob nso, ɔde nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn; mmarima ne mmaa, mmɔfra ne nkɔkoaa, anantwie ne mfunumu ne nnwan nyinaa na ɔde nkrantɛ ano kunkumm wɔn.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Ahitub ba Ahimelek babarima baako a wɔfrɛ no Abiatar firii mu dwane tii Dawid.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Abiatar ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ Saulo akum AWURADE asɔfoɔ no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Abiatar sɛ: Da no a na Edomni Doeg wɔ hɔ no na mehunuu sɛ ɛyɛ deɛn ara a, ɔbɛkɔ akɔka akyerɛ Saulo; me na medi w’agya fie akra nyinaa ho so.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Tena me nkyɛn, nsuro, na deɛ ɔrehwehwɛ me aku me no ara na ɔrehwehwɛ wo nso aku woɔ. Na me nkyɛn deɛ, wɔbɛhwɛ wo so."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Hwɛ, Filistifoɔ ne Keila reko na wɔrefom ayuporebea fa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Dawid bisaa AWURADE sɛ: Menkɔto nhyɛ Filistifoɔ yi so anaa? Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Kɔ na kɔto hyɛ Filistifoɔ no so, na gye Keila.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Dawid mmarima no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, Yuda ha mpo yɛsuro, na nkantom sɛ yɛbɛkɔ Keila akɔne Filistifoɔ dɔm ako.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Dawid kɔɔ so bisaa AWURADE bio. Na AWURADE buaa no sɛ: Sɔre siane kɔ Keila, na me na mede Filistifoɔ no merehyɛ wo nsa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna Dawid ne ne nnipa no sii mu kɔɔ Keila, na ɔne Filistifoɔ no kɔkoeɛ, na ɔkaa wɔn mmoa faeɛ, na ɔkum wɔn ekumkɛseɛ, na Dawid gyee Keilafoɔ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Ahimelek ba Abiatar redwane akɔ Dawid nkyɛn Keila no, na asɔfotadeɛ no kura no, na ɔde siane kɔeɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔkɔka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ Dawid aba Keila. Na Saulo kaa sɛ: Onyankopɔn reyi no ahyɛ me nsa, na wato ne ho mu, sɛ wakɔ kuro a ano wɔ apono ne adaban mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Saulo maa wɔhyiaa ɔman no nyinaa sɛ wɔrekɔ ɔsa na wasiane akɔ Keila akɔtua Dawid ne ne nnipa no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Dawid hunuu sɛ Saulo rebɔ ne ho pɔ bɔne no, ɔka kyerɛɛ Ɔsɔfoɔ Abiatar sɛ: Fa asɔfotadeɛ no bra.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Dawid kaa sɛ: AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn, w’akoa ate no ampa ara sɛ Saulo repɛ aba Keila, na me nti wabɛsɛe kuro no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Keilafoɔ de me bɛhyɛ ne nsa anaa? Saulo bɛsiane aba sɛdeɛ w’akoa teeɛ no? AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn, mekoto mesrɛ wo, ka kyerɛ w’akoa ɛ! Na AWURADE kaa sɛ: Ɔbɛsiane aba.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Dawid kaa sɛ: Keilafoɔ bɛyi me ne me nnipa ahyɛ Saulo nsa? Na AWURADE se: Wɔbɛyi wo ama.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ɛnna Dawid ne ne mmarima a wɔbɛyɛ ahansia no sɔre firii Keila, na wɔkɔɔ baabiara a wɔbɛtumi akorɔ. Na wɔkɔka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ Dawid adwane afiri Keila no, ɔgyaee n’akyiridie.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Dawid kɔtenaa ɛserɛ so bepɔ so atenaeɛ ahodoɔ no mu; na ɔtenaa bepɔ bi so Sif serɛ so. Na Saulo hwehwɛɛ no da biara; nanso Onyankopɔn amfa no anhyɛ ne nsa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Dawid hunuu sɛ Saulo afiri adi rebɛhwehwɛ no aku no. Nso na Dawid wɔ Sif serɛ so wɔ Hores.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna Saulo ba Yonatan sɔre kɔɔ Dawid nkyɛn wɔ Hores, na ɔhyɛɛ ne nsa den Nyankopɔn mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Nsuro, na m’agya Saulo nsa renka wo, na wo na wobɛdi Israel so hene, na mayɛ w’abadiakyire; na m’agya Saulo nso nim yei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔn baanu pamee AWURADE anim. Na Dawid tenaa Hores, na Yonatan kɔɔ ne fie.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ɛnna Sififoɔ foro kɔɔ Saulo nkyɛn Gibea kɔkaa sɛ: Ɛnyɛ Dawid na ɔhunta yɛn nkyɛn wɔ atenaeɛ a ɛwɔ Hores, Hakila kokoɔ a ɛwɔ ɛserɛ pataa no anafoɔ fam no soɔ no?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na afei, ɔhene, siane bra sɛdeɛ wo kra hwehwɛ a ɔrehwehwɛ sɛ ɔbɛsiane no teɛ nyinaa, na yɛn deɛ ne sɛ yɛbɛyi no ahyɛ ɔhene nsa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ɛnna Saulo kaa sɛ: AWURADE nhyira nka mo sɛ moahu me mmɔborɔ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Monkɔ nkɔhwehwɛ mu yie, na monhwɛ nhunu faako a ɔhyɛ ne onii ko a ɔhunuu no hɔ. Na mate sɛ ɔyɛ onitefoɔ sɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na monhwɛ nhu no, faako a ɔhuntahunta no nyinaa, na sɛ ɛyɛ ampa a, monsane mmra me nkyɛn, na me ne mo nkɔ. Na sɛ ɔwɔ asase no so a, mɛtwee mapɛ no Yuda mpempem nyinaa mu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔsɔre dii Saulo anim kɔɔ Sif. Na Dawid ne ne nnipa no wɔ Maon serɛ so, mpaperɛ a ɛwɔ ɛserɛ pataa no anafoɔ fam no so.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Saulo ne ne nnipa kɔɔ sɛ wɔrekɔhwehwɛ no. Na wɔkɔka kyerɛɛ Dawid; na ɔsianee ɔbotan no kɔtenaa Maon serɛ so. Na Saulo teeɛ no, ɔtii Dawid baa Maon serɛ so.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Saulo nam bepɔ no fa ha, na Dawid ne ne nnipa nso nam bepɔ no fa ha; na Dawid repɛ ntɛm afiri Saulo anim akorɔ no, Saulo ne ne nnipa no twaa Dawid ne ne nnipa no ho hyiae sɛ wɔrekye wɔn.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɔbɔfoɔ bi baa Saulo nkyɛn bɛkaa sɛ: Ka wo ho bra, na Filistifoɔ abɛgu asase no so.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Enti Saulo sane firi Dawid akyi kɔ kɔhyiaa Filistifoɔ no; enti wɔfrɛ hɔ sɛ Dwaneeɛ Botan.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Dawid firi hɔ foro kɔtenaa En-gedi bepɔ so atenaeɛ mu."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Saulo sane firii Filistifoɔ akyi baeɛ no, wɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, Dawid wɔ En-gedi serɛ so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛnna Saulo faa mmarima mpensa a wɔayi wɔn afiri Israel nyinaa mu, na ɔkɔɔ sɛ ɔrekɔhwehwɛ Dawid ne ne nnipa no Nkakragya Abotan soɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔduruu nnwammuo a ɛwɔ ɛkwan no soɔ no ho; na ɔbodan bi wɔ hɔ, na Saulo hyɛnee mu sɛ ɔrekɔgya ne nan. Na Dawid ne ne nnipa nso tete ɔbodan no mu nohoa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Dawid nnipa no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, da a AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ wo sɛ: Hwɛ, mede wo tamfo bɛhyɛ wo nsa, na woayɛ no sɛdeɛ ɛyɛ wɔ w’ani soɔ, no nie. Ɛnna Dawid sɔre wiawiaa ne ho kɔtwaa Saulo batakari ano.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛno akyiri no, Dawid akoma bɔɔ no paripari sɛ watwa Saulo atadeɛ ano.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ ne nnipa no sɛ: AWURADE mma no mpare me sɛ mɛyɛ me wura a AWURADE asra no no adeɛ a ɛte sɛɛ, sɛ mɛtene me nsa maka no, ɛfiri sɛ deɛ AWURADE asra no ne no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Dawid de nsɛm yi bɔɔ ne nnipa no pem, na wampene amma wɔansɔre antia Saulo. Na Saulo sɔre firii ɔbodan no mu sii ne kwan so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɛno akyiri no, Dawid nso sɔre firii ɔbodan no mu firii adi, na ɔhyɛɛ Saulo mmɔn sɛ: Me wura, ɔhene! Na Saulo hwɛɛ n’akyiri no, Dawid bɔɔ ne tiri ase na ɔkotoe;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Adɛn nti na wotie nnipa nsɛm a wɔkeka sɛ: Hwɛ, Dawid pɛ wo bɔne, no?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hwɛ, ɛnnɛ da yi w’ani ahunu sɛdeɛ AWURADE de wo hyɛɛ me nsa nnɛ ɔbodan no mu; na wɔkaa sɛ menku wo, na medodoo wo ho, na mese: Merentene me nsa menka me wura, ɛfiri sɛ deɛ AWURADE asra no ne no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nso, m’agya, ampa ara, hwɛ sɛ wo batakari ano kura me nsam. Na ɛnam sɛ matwa wo batakari ano na manku woɔ yi, hunu na hwɛ sɛ bɔne anaa mmarato bi nni me nsam; na menyɛɛ wo bɔne biara, nso wo deɛ, worepɛ me aku me.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> AWURADE mmu me ne wo ntam atɛn, na AWURADE nnye m’aweretɔdeɛ wo nsam. Na me nsa deɛ, ɛrenka wo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sɛdeɛ tete bɛ no ka no “Abɔnefoɔ so na bɔne fire”, na me nsa deɛ, ɛrenka wo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hwan akyi na Israel hene atu die yi? Hwan na woreti no yi? Ɔkraman funu akyi, ɔkraman dwie baako akyi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na AWURADE nyɛ ɔtemmufoɔ, na ɔmmu me ne wo ntam atɛn, na ɔnhunu na ɔnni m’asɛm mma me, na ɔmmu me atɛn nyi me wo nsam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Dawid kaa nsɛm yi kyerɛɛ Saulo wieeɛ no, Saulo kaa sɛ: Wo nne nie, me ba Dawid? Na Saulo maa ne nne so suiɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Wotene kyɛne me, ɛfiri sɛ wode papa atua me ka, na me deɛ, mede bɔne matua wo ka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na woakyerɛ me nnɛ sɛ wo ne me adi no yie, sɛ AWURADE de me hyɛɛ wo nsa na woanku me.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na sɛ obi to ne tamfo a, ɔbɛma no de ne ho sɔnn akɔ anaa? Enti AWURADE ntua wo ka pa nhyɛ deɛ woayɛ me nnɛ yi ananmu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na afei, hwɛ, menim sɛ wobɛdi hene, na Israel ahennie bɛtim wɔ wo nsam;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na afei ka me AWURADE ntam sɛ worentwa m’asefoɔ a wɔbɛdi m’akyire ngu, na worempepa me din mfiri m’agya fie.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Dawid kaa Saulo ntam no. Na Saulo sii mu kɔɔ fie; na Dawid ne ne nnipa no foro kɔɔ bepɔ so atenaeɛ no mu."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Samuel wuiɛ; na Israel nyinaa boaboaa wɔn ano bɛgyamm no, na wɔkoraa no ne fie wɔ Rama. Na Dawid sɔre siane kɔɔ Paran serɛ so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔbarima bi wɔ Maon a n’adwuma wɔ Karmel, na ɔbarima no yɛ onipa kɛseɛ; ɔwɔ nnwan mpensa ne mmirekyie apem; na ɔretwitwa ne nnwan ho wɔ Karmel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔbarima no din de Nabal, na ne yere din de Abigail; na ɔbaa no wɔ adwempa, na ne ho nso yɛ fɛ; na ɔbarima no deɛ, na ɔyɛ den, na ne nneyɛɛ nyɛ; na ɔyɛ Kalebni.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Dawid tee no ɛserɛ so hɔ sɛ Nabal retwitwa ne nnwan ho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Dawid somaa mmeranteɛ du, na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ mmeranteɛ no sɛ: Momforo nkɔ Karmel na monkɔ Nabal nkyɛn, na monkɔbɔ me din nkyea no mma me.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na monse no sɛ: Asomdwoeɛ nka wo, asomdwoeɛ nka wo fie, na asomdwoeɛ nka deɛ wowɔ nyinaa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na afei, mate sɛ wowɔ nnwan ho twitwafoɔ; afei wo nnwanhwɛfoɔ a wowɔ wɔn no ne yɛn tenaeɛ no, yɛampoopoo wɔn, na wɔn biribiara nso anyera berɛ a wɔtenaa Karmel no nyinaa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bisabisa wo mmeranteɛ no na wɔbɛka akyerɛ wo; enti ma mmeranteɛ no nnya w’anim adom, na afahyɛ da na yɛaba yi, fa deɛ ɛwɔ wo nsam ma wo nkoa ne wo ba Dawid ɛ!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Dawid mmeranteɛ no duruiɛ no, wɔde Dawid din kaa nsɛm yi nyinaa kyerɛɛ Nabal, na wɔtwɛneeɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Nabal buaa Dawid nkoa no sɛ: Hwan ne Dawid, na hwan ne Yisai ba? Ɛnnɛ nkoa a wɔtete wɔn ho firi wɔn wuranom ho dɔɔso.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na memfa m’aduane ne me nsuo ne me nam a makum de rema me nnwan ho twitwafoɔ no memma nnipa a mennim deɛ wɔfire anaa?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna Dawid mmeranteɛ no danee wɔn ho sii kwan soɔ, na wɔsane bɛkaa nsɛm yi nyinaa kyerɛɛ no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ɛnna Dawid ka kyerɛɛ ne nnipa no sɛ: Mo nyinaa mmobɔ mo nkrantɛ mo asenem. Na wɔn nyinaa bobɔɔ wɔn nkrantɛ, na Dawid nso bɔɔ ne nkrantɛ, na ɛbɛyɛ mmarima ahanan foro dii Dawid akyi, na ahanu tenaa nnoɔma no ho.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mmeranteɛ no mu baako kɔka kyerɛɛ Nabal yere Abigail sɛ: Hwɛ, Dawid somaa abɔfoɔ firi ɛserɛ so bɛkyeaa yɛn wura, na ɔpoopoo wɔn.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nso nnipa no yɛ ma yɛn sɛ, na wɔanyɛ yɛn bɔne biara, na yɛwɔ wiram hɔ a yɛne wɔn nam no nyinaa, yɛn biribiara anyera da;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> wɔyɛɛ yɛn ho fasuo anadwo ne awia berɛ a yɛne wɔn teɛ a yɛrehwɛ nnwan no nyinaa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na afei hwɛ, na dwene deɛ wobɛyɛ, na wɔakyere yɛn wura ne ne fie nyinaa so sa bɔne, nso ɔyɛ ɔba huhuni a obi ntumi nkasa nkyerɛ no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna Abigail yɛɛ ntɛm faa paanoo ahanu ne nsa nkotokuo mmienu ma, ne nnwan nnum a wɔasiesie wɔn ne nkyeweɛ susuoadeɛ nnum ne bobe aba a wɔabɔ no ntoantoa ahanu de soaa mfunumu,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ ne mmeranteɛ no sɛ: Monsene nni m’anim, hwɛ, meredi mo akyiri maba. Na ne kunu Nabal deɛ, wanka ankyerɛ no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ ɔte afunumu so resiane aba bepɔ no aseɛ no, hwɛ, na Dawid ne ne nnipa no nso resiane hyia no, na ɔhyiaa wɔn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nso na Dawid aka sɛ: Kwa ara kwa na mahwɛ oyi adeɛ a ɔwɔ no ɛserɛ so nyinaa soɔ, na deɛ ɛyɛ ne deɛ nyinaa mu biribiara anyera, nso bɔne na ɔde ahyɛ me papa ananmu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sɛ ɛkɔsi ɔkyena anɔpa, megya n’adeɛ a ɔwɔ nyinaa mu onini baako sei mpo a, Onyankopɔn nyɛ Dawid atamfoɔ saa na ɔnka ho saa!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Abigail hunuu Dawid no, ɔyɛɛ ntɛm firii n’afunumu so sii fam, na ɔde n’anim butuu Dawid anim, na ɔbɔɔ ne mu ase kɔɔ fam,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na ɔde ne ho hwee ne nan ase kaa sɛ: Me wura, me so na amumuyɛ yi nna, na ma w’afenaa nkasa ngu w’aso mu ɛ, na tie w’afenaa nsɛm.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mesrɛ wo, mma me wura mmfa n’akoma nnto onipa huhuni Nabal yi so, na sɛ ne din teɛ no, sɛ ɔteɛ ara ne no, Nabal ne ne din, agyegyentwisɛm wɔ ne mu; na me, w’afenaa deɛ, manhunu me wura mmeranteɛ a wosomaa wɔn no.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na afei, me wura, sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ na wo kra te aseɛ yi, AWURADE asianka wo, na woammɛdi mogya ho so sɛ wode wo ara wo nsa bɛtɔ were. Na afei ma w’atamfo ne wɔn a wɔpɛ me wura bɔne no nyɛ sɛ Nabal.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na afei, akyɛdeɛ a w’afenaa de abrɛ me wura yi, ma wɔmfa mma mmeranteɛ a wɔdi me wura akyire no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Fa ɛso yi kyɛ w’afenaa ɛ! Na ampa ara AWURADE bɛkyekyere efie a atim ama me wura, ɛfiri sɛ me wura reko ama AWURADE, na wɔrenhunu wo mu bɔne biara wo nna nyinaa.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na sɛ onipa asɔre reti wo na wahwehwɛ wo aku wo a, ɛnneɛ wɔnkyekyere me wura kra, nkwa boaa mu, AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn nkyɛn, na w’atamfo kra deɛ, wɔnto no sɛ adeɛ a ɛfiri ntɔmmoɔ mu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE nya yɛ me wura papa a waka wɔ wo ho no nyinaa na ɔde wo si Israel so hene a,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> me wura werɛ renho na n’akoma remmɔ no paripari sɛ waka mogya agu kwa anaa sɛ me wura no ara atɔ were. Na AWURADE bɛyɛ me wura yie, na woakae w’afenaa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ɛnna Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Abigail sɛ: Nhyira nka AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn a ɔsomaa wo maa wobɛhyiaa me nnɛ yi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na nhyira nka w’adwempa, na nhyira nka wo sɛ woasianka me nnɛ da yi na mankɔdi mogya ho so, na mamfa me ara me nsa mantɔ were.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ampa ara, sɛ AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn a wasianka me na manyɛ wo bɔne no te aseɛ yi, sɛ woanyɛ ntɛm ammɛhyia me a, anka ɛbɛduru ɔkyena anɔpa, obiara a ɔyɛ onini renka mma Nabal.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ɛnna Dawid gyee deɛ ɔde brɛɛ no no ne nsam, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Foro kɔ wo fie asomdwoeɛ mu, hwɛ, matie wo, na mahwɛ w’anim.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na Abigail kɔɔ Nabal nkyɛn, na hwɛ, wato ne ho pono ne fie hɔ sɛ ɔhene pono na Nabal ani agye ne ho, na waboro titaa. Na wanka no hwee kɔsii sɛ adeɛ kyeeɛ.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na anɔpa nsa tetee Nabal ani soɔ no, ne yere kaa nsɛm yi nyinaa kyerɛɛ no, na n’akoma gyenee wɔ ne yam, na ɔdanee sɛ ɔboɔ.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na ɛbɛyɛ dadu no, AWURADE bɔɔ Nabal, na ɔwuiɛ.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na Dawid tee sɛ Nabal awuo no, ɔkaa sɛ: Nhyira nka AWURADE a watɔ Nabal nsopa so were ama me na wasɔ n’akoa mu afiri bɔne ho, na AWURADE adane Nabal bɔne agu n’atifi! Na Dawid soma maa wɔne Abigail kɔkasaa sɛ ɔbɛfa no aware.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na Dawid nkoa no duruu Abigail nkyɛn Karmel kɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Dawid asoma yɛn wo nkyɛn sɛ ɔrebɛfa wo aware.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na ɔsɔre bɔɔ ne tiri ase kotoe kaa sɛ: Hwɛ, w’afenaa yɛ abaawa a ɔbɛhohoro me wura nkoa nan ho.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na Abigail yɛɛ ntɛm sɔre tenaa afunumu so, ne mmaawa baanum a wɔnenam ne nan aseɛ, na ɔdii Dawid abɔfoɔ no akyi kɔyɛɛ ne yere.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na Dawid waree Ahinoam a ɔfirii Yesreel nso, na wɔn baanu no yɛɛ ne yerenom.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na Saulo de ne ba Mikal, Dawid yere no, ama Lais ba Palti a ɔfiri Galim."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Sififoɔ baa Saulo nkyɛn Gibea bɛkaa sɛ: Ɛnyɛ Dawid na ɔhunta Hakila kokoɔ a ɛkyerɛ pataa no anim no soɔ no?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛnna Saulo sɔre siane kɔɔ Sif serɛ soɔ, ɔne Israel mmarima mpensa a wɔayi wɔn, sɛ ɔrekɔhwehwɛ Dawid Sif serɛ so.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Saulo kyeree nsraban Hakila kokoɔ a ɛkyerɛ ɛserɛ pataa no anim no so, ɛkwan ho, na Dawid deɛ, ɔtenaa ɛserɛ no so, na ɔhunuu sɛ Saulo reti no aba ɛserɛ no so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Dawid somaa akwansrafoɔ, na ɔhunuu sɛ Saulo aba ampa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna Dawid sɔre kɔɔ deɛ Saulo akyere nsraban hɔ. Na Dawid hunuu faako a Saulo ne ne sahene Ner ba Abner deda; nso Saulo da nteaseɛnam aboaeɛ hɔ, na ɛdɔm no akyere nsraban atwa ne ho ahyia.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Hetini Ahimelek ne Seruia ba Abisai, Yoab nua sɛ: Hwan na ɔne me bɛsiane akɔ Saulo nkyɛn wɔ nsra mu hɔ? Na Abisai sɛ: Mene wo bɛsiane akɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Dawid ne Abisai kɔɔ ɛdɔm no nkyɛn anadwo, na hwɛ Saulo da hɔ ada, nteaseɛnam aboaeɛ hɔ, na ne pea si fam wɔ n’atifi. Na Abner ne dɔm no deda ne ho hyia.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Abisai ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Onyankopɔn de wo tamfo ahyɛ wo nsa nnɛ, na afei ma memfa pea no menwɔ no nhwire ne mu nsi fam prɛko, na meremfoa no so.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Abisai sɛ: Nku no, na hwan na ɔtene ne nsa ka deɛ AWURADE asra no na ɔdi bem?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Dawid kaa sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ yi, gye AWURADE na ɔbɛbɔ no ahwe; sɛ ne da bɛduru na wawu, anaasɛ ɔbɛkɔ ɔsa na apra no akɔ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> AWURADE mma no mpare me sɛ mɛtene me nsa maka deɛ AWURADE asra no no. Na afei fa pea a ɛwɔ n’atifi no ne nsuo kuruwa no na yɛnkɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna Dawid faa pea ne nsuo kuruwa no firii Saulo atifi, na wɔkɔe: Na obiara anhunu, na obiara ante, na obiara annyane, na na wɔn nyinaa adeda, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE nnahɔɔ atotɔ wɔn so.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Dawid sene kɔɔ ɔfa nohoa, na ɔkɔgyinaa bepɔ no atifi wɔ akyirikyiri a kwan pa ara da wɔn ntam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Dawid hyɛɛ ɛdɔm no ne Ner ba Abner mmɔn sɛ: Abner ee! Wonnye so? Ɛnna Abner gyee so sɛ: Ɛyɛ wo hwan na worehyɛ ɔhene mmɔn no?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Abner sɛ: Wonyɛ ɔbarima anaa? Na hwan na ɔte sɛ woɔ wɔ Israel mu? Na adɛn nti na woanwɛn wo wura ɔhene? Na ɛdɔm no mu bi baa sɛ anka ɔrebɛkum wo wura ɔhene.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Asɛm a woadie yi nyɛ. Sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ yi, mosɛ wuo, sɛ moanwɛn mo wura a AWURADE asra no no. Na afei, hwɛ deɛ ɔhene pea ne nsuo kuruwa a ɛsisi n’atifi no wɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnna Saulo hunuu sɛ ɛyɛ Dawid nne, na ɔkaa sɛ: Wo nne nie, me ba Dawid? Na Dawid se: Ɛyɛ me nne, me wura ɔhene.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: Adɛn nti na me wura di n’akoa akyiri seyie? Mayɛ dɛn? Anaasɛ bɔne bɛn na ɛwɔ me nsam?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Enti afei ma me wura ɔhene ntie n’akoa nsɛm. Sɛ AWURADE na wahwanyan wo atia me a, ɛnneɛ ma no nnye afɔdeɛ. Na sɛ ɛyɛ nnipa mma deɛ a, wɔadome wɔn, AWURADE anim, sɛ wɔapamo me nnɛ sɛ merennya kyɛfa wɔ AWURADE agyapadeɛ no ho, na wɔse: Kɔ na kɔsom anyame foforɔ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Enti afei wɔmmma me mogya nngu fam wɔ faako a ɛnyɛ AWURADE anim, ɛfiri sɛ Israel hene afiri adi rehwehwɛ ɔkraman dwie, sɛdeɛ wɔti akokɔhwedeɛ wɔ mmepɔ soɔ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ɛnna Saulo kaa sɛ: Mayɛ bɔne, sane bra, me ba Dawid, na merenyɛ wo bɔne bio, ɛfiri sɛ me kra boɔ ayɛ den w’ani so nnɛ da yi. Hwɛ, madi nkwaseasɛm na mafom bebree pa ara.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Dawid buaa sɛ: Hwɛ, ɔhene pea nie, na ma mmeranteɛ no mu baako mmra mmɛfa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na AWURADE bɛdane onipa biara tenenee ne ne nokorɛdie ama no, sɛ nnɛ AWURADE de wo hyɛɛ me nsa, na mampɛ sɛ metene me nsa meka deɛ AWURADE asra no no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na hwɛ, sɛdeɛ wo kra asom boɔ nnɛ m’ani soɔ yi, saa ara na me kra nso nsom boɔ AWURADE ani soɔ, na ɔnyi me mfiri ahohiahia nyinaa mu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Nhyira nka wo, me ba Dawid. Wobɛyɛ nnoɔma pii, na wobɛdi nim wɔ ne nyinaa mu nso. Ɛnna Dawid sii ne kwan soɔ. Na Saulo sane kɔɔ ne tenabea."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Dawid see no n’akoma mu sɛ: Anhwɛ a, da bi, Saulo nsa na ɛbɛku me; biribiara nyɛ mma me sɛ mɛdwane akɔ Filistifoɔ asase soɔ, na Saulo agyaa me na wanhwehwɛ me bio Israel asase nyinaa so, na mafiri ne nsa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Dawid sɔreeɛ, na ɔne mmarima ahansia a wɔka ne ho no twaa mu kɔɔ Gathene Maok ba Akis nkyɛn.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Dawid ne Akis tenaa Gat, ɔno ne ne mmarima no, obiara ne ne fiefoɔ, Dawid ne ne yerenom baanu no, Yesreelni Ahinoam ne Karmelni Abigail, Nabal yere no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Dawid adwane kɔ Gat; na wankɔ so anhwehwɛ no bio.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Akis sɛ: Sɛ manya w’anim adom a, ma wɔmma me tenabea bi wiram nkuro no bi mu, na menkɔtena hɔ: Na adɛn nti na w’akoa ne wo ntena ahenkuro mu?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna Akis de Siklag maa no da no ara; enti Siklag danee Yuda ahemfo deɛ de bɛsi nnɛ yi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na nna a Dawid de tenaa Filistifoɔ asase soɔ no yɛ afirinhyia ne abosome nnan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Dawid ne ne mmarima no kɔ kɔtuaa Gesurfoɔ ne Girsifoɔ ne Amalekfoɔ; na wɔn na na wɔtete asase no soɔ firi teteete de kɔduru Sur a ɛda kɔ Misraim asase soɔ no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Dawid bɔɔ asase no, na wannya ɔbarima anaa ɔbaa anikan, na ɔfaa nnwan ne anantwie ne mfunumu ne yoma ne ntadeɛ, na ɔsane baa Akis nkyɛn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Akis kaa sɛ: Ɛhefoɔ na ɛnnɛ mokɔfom wɔn faeɛ yi? Na Dawid se: Yɛkɔɔ Yuda Negeb ne Yerahmeelfoɔ anafoɔ fam ne Kenifoɔ anafoɔ fam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Dawid annya ɔbarima anaa ɔbaa bi anikan sɛ ɔde wɔn bɛba Gat, ɛfiri sɛ ɔse: Anyɛ a, wɔbɛka yɛn ho asɛm sɛ: Sɛɛ na Dawid ayɛ. Na nna a ɔde tenaa Filistifoɔ asase soɔ no nyinaa sɛ ɔyɛeɛ ara ne no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Akis gyee Dawid diiɛ kaa sɛ: Wama ne ho abɔn ne man Israel pa ara, enti ɔbɛyɛ m’akoa daa."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na saa berɛ no Filistifoɔ boaboaa wɔn dɔm ano sɛ wɔretu sa ne Israel akɔko. Na Akis ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Hunu pefee sɛ wo ne wo mmammarima no ne me na ɛbɛkɔ ɔsa yi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Akis sɛ: Ɛnneɛ wobɛhunu deɛ w’akoa bɛyɛ. Na Akis ka kyerɛɛ Dawid sɛ: Ɔyɛ, me nso mede wo bɛyɛ me tiri wɛmfoɔ nna nyinaa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Saa berɛ yi na Samuel awu ama Israel nyinaa asu no asie no Rama, ɔno ara ne kuro mu. Na Saulo atu asamanfrɛfoɔ ne asumanfoɔ nyinaa afiri asase no so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Filistifoɔ no boaboaa wɔn ano ba bɛkyeree nsraban Sunem. Na Saulo boaboaa Israelfoɔ nyinaa ano, na wɔkyeree nsraban Gilboa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Saulo hunuu Filistifoɔ nsraban no no, ɔsuroeɛ, na n’akoma tuu papaapa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Saulo kɔbisaa AWURADE, nanso daeɛ mu oo, Urim ntonto so oo, adiyifoɔ anomu oo, AWURADE ammua no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnna Saulo ka kyerɛɛ ne nkoa sɛ: Monkɔhwehwɛ ɔbaa samanfrɛni bi mma me, na menkɔ ne hɔ abisa. Na ne nkoa no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, ɔbaa samanfrɛni bi wɔ Endor.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Saulo sakyeraa ne ho hyɛɛ atadeɛ foforɔ, na ɔsii mu kɔeɛ a na nnipa baanu ka ne ho, na wɔduruu ɔbaa no nkyɛn anadwo; na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Fa ɔsamanfrɛ so hyɛ me nkɔm, na ma deɛ mɛbɔ ne din makyerɛ woɔ no mforo mmra mma me.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔbaa no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, wo ara wonim deɛ Saulo ayɛ, sɛdeɛ watwitwa asamanfrɛfoɔ ne adunsinfoɔ afiri asase yi soɔ, na adɛn nti na woresum me kra fidie ama wɔaku me yi?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Saulo kaa no AWURADE ntam sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ yi, worenni asɛm yi mu so biara.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna ɔbaa no kaa sɛ: Hwan na memma no mforo mmra mma woɔ? Na ɔse: Ma Samuel mforo mmra mma me.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔbaa no hunuu Samuel no, ɔde nne kɛseɛ teaa mu; na ɔbaa no ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Adɛn nti na woadaadaa me yi? Na wone Saulo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔhene ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Nsuro! Na ɛdeɛn na wohunu? Na ɔbaa no se: Onyame bi na mehunu sɛ ɔfiri asase mu reforo ba.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ne su te sɛn? Na ɔse: Akɔkoraa bi a ɔhyɛ atadeɛ yuu na ɔreforo ba. Na Saulo hunuu sɛ ɛyɛ Samuel, na ɔbɔɔ ne mu ase koto sɔree no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Samuel ka kyerɛɛ Saulo sɛ: Adɛn nti na wohaa me maa meforo baeɛ yi? Na Saulo buaa sɛ: Me ho hiahia me papaapa, na Filistifoɔ ne me reko, na Onyankopɔn apa m’akyi, na ɔmmua me bio; ɔmfa adiyifoɔ so, na ɔmfa daeɛ mu nso, enti na mafrɛ woɔ yi, sɛ kyerɛ me deɛ menyɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Samuel kaa sɛ: Adɛn nti na wonim sɛ AWURADE apa w’akyire na wadane wo tamfo na wobisa me adeɛ yi?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na AWURADE ayɛ sɛdeɛ ɔnam me so kaeɛ no, na AWURADE ahwam wo nsam ahennie no de akɔma wo yɔnko Dawid.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ woantie AWURADE nne na woanyɛ n’abufuhyeɛ so adeɛ Amalekfoɔ soɔ nti, na AWURADE ayɛ wo ɛso adeɛ nnɛ yi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na AWURADE de Israel nso ne wo bɛhyɛ Filistifoɔ nsa; na ɔkyena wo ne wo mma bɛba abɛka me ho, na AWURADE de Israel dɔm nso bɛhyɛ Filistifoɔ nsa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛnna ntɛm ara Saulo hwee ase bankwaa birim, na Samuel nsɛm no nti ɔsuroo papaapa, nso na ahoɔden biara nni ne mu, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔnnidii da mu no nyinaa ne anadwo mu no nyinaa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔbaa no baa Saulo nkyɛn, na ɔhunuu sɛ wabɔ hu, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, w’afenaa atie wo, na mede me nkwa mato me nsam, na matie wo nsɛm a woka kyerɛɛ me no,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na wo nso tie w’afenaa, na ma memfa paanoo sini memmɛsi w’anim, na di, na woanya ahoɔden de asi wo kwan so akɔ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wampene kaa sɛ: Merenni. Na ne nkoa ne ɔbaa no nso hyɛɛ no, na ɔtiee wɔn, na ɔsɔree firii fam tenaa mpa so.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nso na ɔbaa no wɔ nantwie ba a wadɔre wɔ efie hɔ, na ɔyɛɛ ntɛm kumm no, na ɔfaa esiam forɔe, na ɔde too apiti;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> na ɔde bɛsii Saulo ne ne nkoa no anim na wɔdiiɛ; na wɔsɔre sii mu kɔe anadwo no."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Afei Filistifoɔ boaboaa wɔn dɔm nyinaa ano baa Afek, na Israelfoɔ kɔkyeree nsraban nsuo aniwa a ɛwɔ Yesreel ho.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Filistifoɔ asafohene bɛtwaa mu, ɔha ɔha ne apem apem so, na Dawid ne ne mmarima no ka Akis ho bɛtwaa mu wɔ kyidɔm no mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɛnna Filistifoɔ asafohene no kaa sɛ: Na Hebrifoɔ yi ɛ? Na Akis ka kyerɛɛ Filistifoɔ asafohene no sɛ: Ɛnyɛ Dawid, Israelhene Saulo akoa a ɔne me atena nna sɛɛ anaa mfeɛ sɛɛ yi a menhunuu ne ho bɔne biara firi da a ɔwaeeɛ de bɛsi nnɛ no nie?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Filistifoɔ asafohene no bo fuu no, na Filistifoɔ asafohene no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ma ɔbarima yi nsane, na ɔnsane nkɔ ne tenabea a wode no tenaeɛ hɔ, na mma ɔne yɛn nnkɔ ɔsa no, na wannane n’ani ankyerɛ yɛn ɔko no mu; na ɛdeɛn na oyi de bɛpata ne wura? Ɛnyɛ nnipa yi ti?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnyɛ Dawid a wɔgyee ne ho dwom soɔ asa mu sɛ: Saulo akum n’apem na Dawid akum ne mpem du no nie anaa?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna Akis frɛɛ Dawid ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ yi, wotene, na me deɛ, anka ɛyɛ ma me sɛ wo ne me bɛdi akɔneaba ɔsa yi mu; ɛfiri sɛ ɛfiri da a wobaa me nkyɛn de bɛsi nnɛ menhunuu wo ho bɔne biara; na asafohene no na ɛmpɛ woɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Enti sane, na kɔ asomdwoeɛ mu, na wo ho anyɛ Filistifoɔ no ahi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Akis sɛ: Na mayɛ dɛn, na ɛdeɛn na woahu no w’akoa ho firi da a mebaa w’anim de abɛsi nnɛ yi a enti mennkɔ na me ne me wura ɔhene atamfoɔ nnkɔko yi?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Akis bua see Dawid sɛ: Menim sɛ woyɛ wɔ m’ani so sɛ Nyankopɔn bɔfoɔ; nso Filistifoɔ asafohene no na wɔse: Ɔne yɛn renkɔ ɔsa no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Enti monsɔre anɔpahema, wo ne wo wura nkoa a wɔne wo baeɛ no, na mosɔre nhema na anim tete ara pɛ a, moasim akɔ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna Dawid ne ne mmarima no tuaa nhema sii mu sɛ wɔresane akɔ Filistifoɔ asase so. Na Filistifoɔ no baa Yesreel."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Dawid ne ne mmarima no duruu Siklag da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no, na Amalekfoɔ abɛtua anafoɔ fam ne Siklag, na wɔabɔ Siklag, na wɔde ogya ahye.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔafa mmaa a wɔwɔ mu no nnommum, firi mmɔfra so kɔsi mpanin so, wɔankum obiara, na wɔsoaa wɔn sii kwan so kɔeɛ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Dawid ne ne mmarima no duruu kuro no mu no, na hwɛ, wɔde ogya ahye, na wɔn yerenom ne wɔn mmammarima ne wɔn mmammaa no, wɔafa wɔn nnommum kɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna Dawid ne dɔm a wɔka ne ho no memaa wɔn nne so sui ara kɔsii sɛ wɔannya ahoɔden ansu bio.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Dawid yerenom baanu no, Yesreelni Ahinoam ne Karmelni Abigail, Nabal yere no, nso wɔafa wɔn nnommum bi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Dawid ho kyeree no papaapa, ɛfiri sɛ ɛdɔm no kaa sɛ wɔbɛsi no aboɔ, na ɛdɔm no nyinaa kra botoeɛ, wɔn mmammarima ne wɔn mmammaa nti; nanso Dawid hyɛɛ ne ho den AWURADE Nyankopɔn mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ Ɔsɔfoɔ Ahimelek ba Abiatar sɛ: Fa asɔfotadeɛ no brɛ me. Na Abiatar de asɔfotadeɛ no brɛɛ Dawid.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Dawid bisaa AWURADE sɛ: Menti ɛdɔm yi anaa? Mɛto wɔn? Na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ti wɔn, na wobɛto wɔn, na gyeɛ nso wobɛgye.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnna Dawid sii mu kɔeɛ, ɔno ne mmarima ahansia a wɔka ne ho no. Na wɔduruu Besor subonhwa ho no, wɔn a wɔkaa akyire no soo hɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Dawid ne mmarima ahanan tii wɔn, na ahanu a wɔabrɛ a wɔantumi antwa Besor subonhwa no soo hɔ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔhunuu Misraimni bi wiram hɔ, na wɔde no brɛɛ Dawid; na wɔmaa no paanoo diiɛ, na wɔmaa no nsuo nomeeɛ,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na wɔmaa no borɔdɔma ɛtoa sini ne bobe aba ntoa ntoa mmienu; na ɔdiiɛ no, n’ani so baee no, ɛfiri sɛ nnansa awia ne anadwo na ɔnnidiiɛ na ɔnnomee.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwan nipa ne wo, na ɛhe na wofire? Na ɔse: Meyɛ Misraimni ba, Amalekni bi akoa, na me wura gyaa me hɔ, ɛfiri sɛ yadeɛ bɔɔ me nnaano.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Yɛkɔtuaa Keretifoɔ anafoɔ fam ne deɛ ɛyɛ Yuda dea no ne Kaleb anafoɔ fam, na yɛde ogya hyee Siklag.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Dawid ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Wode me bɛsiane akɔ ɛdɔm no nkyɛn? Na ɔse: Ka me Onyankopɔn sɛ worenku me, nso woremfa me nhyɛ me wura nsa, na mede wo bɛsiane akɔ ɛdɔm no nkyɛn.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔde no siane kɔeɛ; na hwɛ, asadeɛ bebrebe a wɔakɔfa no Filistifoɔ asase soɔ ne Yuda asase soɔ no nti, wɔboaboa fam hɔ nyinaa a na wɔredidi na wɔrenom na wɔresa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Dawid kunkumm wɔn firi ahemadakye kɔsii da a ɛdi soɔ no anwummerɛ; na wɔn mu biara amfiri mu amfi gye mmeranteɛ ahanan a wɔtenatenaa yoma so dwaneeɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Dawid gyee deɛ Amalekfoɔ faeɛ no nyinaa; ne yerenom baanu no nso, Dawid gyee wɔn;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na anka wɔn biribiara, ketewa oo, kɛseɛ oo, mmammarima oo, mmammaa oo, asadeɛ a wɔbɛfaeɛ no mu biara oo, Dawid de ne nyinaa sane bae.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Dawid faa nnwan ne anantwie no nyinaa, na wɔde wɔn dii mmoa no anim baeɛ, na wɔkaa sɛ: Yei deɛ, Dawid asadeɛ nie!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Dawid duruu mmarima ahanu a wɔabrɛ a wɔantumi anni Dawid akyire a wɔgyaa wɔn tenaa Besor subonhwa ho no nkyɛn. Na wɔfirii adi bɛhyiaa Dawid ne ɛdɔm a wɔne no nam no, na Dawid pinkyɛɛ ɛdɔm no kyeaa wɔn.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna mmarima a wɔne Dawid kɔeɛ no mu nnipa bɔne ne ahuhufoɔ buaa sɛ: Ɛnam sɛ wɔne yɛn ankɔ nti, wɔremma wɔn asadeɛ a yɛakɔgyeɛ no bi, gye wɔn yerenom ne wɔn mma na wɔmfa wɔn nkorɔ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Dawid kaa sɛ: Anuanom, monnyɛ saa, deɛ AWURADE de ama yɛn ho, na wahwɛ yɛn soɔ, na ɔde dɔm a wɔbaa yɛn soɔ no ahyɛ yɛn nsa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na hwan na ɔbɛtie mo, asɛm yi mu? Na sɛ deɛ ɔkɔ akono kyɛfa teɛ no, saa ara na deɛ ɔtenaa nnoɔma ho no nso kyɛfa teɛ, wɔnkyɛ mu pɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɛfiri da no ara de rekorɔ no, ɔde too hɔ yɛɛ ahyɛdeɛ ne atemmudeɛ maa Israel de bɛsi nnɛ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Dawid duruu Siklag no, ɔsoma maa wɔde asadeɛ no bi kɔmaa Yuda mpanin a wɔyɛ ne nnamfo kaa sɛ: Hwɛ, AWURADE atamfoɔ asadeɛ mu akyɛdeɛ a wɔde rebrɛ mo nie.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ɔde kɔmaa wɔn a wɔwɔ Betel ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Ramot a ɛwɔ Negeb ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Yatir,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Aroer ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Sifmot ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Estemoa,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Rakal ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Yerahmeelfoɔ nkuro mu, ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Kenifoɔ kuro mu,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Horma ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Kor-asan ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Atak,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Hebron, ne mmeammea a Dawid ne ne nnipa kyinkyiniiɛ hɔ."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Filistifoɔ ne Israel koeɛ; na Israel mmarima dwanee Filistifoɔ anim, na wɔtotɔe Gilboa bepɔ so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Filistifoɔ tu saa Saulo ne ne mma, na Filistifoɔ no kumm Saulo mma Yonatan ne Abinadab ne Malkisua.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔko no denee Saulo, na agyantofoɔ, mmarima a wɔkura tadua no hunuu no, na wɔtoo no piraa no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Saulo ka kyerɛɛ n’akodeɛkurani sɛ: Twe wo nkrantɛ fa wɔ me, na momonotofoɔ yi amma ammɛwɔ me na wɔammɛgoro me atɔprɛ. Na n’akodeɛkurani no ampene, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔsuro pii. Ɛnna Saulo faa nkrantɛ na ɔhwee soɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na n’akodeɛkurani no hunuu sɛ Saulo awuo no, ɔno nso hwee ne nkrantɛ so saa ara, na ɔne no wui.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Saa ara na Saulo ne ne mma baasa ne n’akodeɛkurani ne ne mmarima nyinaa nso wuwuu prɛko da no ara.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Israel mmarima a wɔwɔ bonhwa no agya ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Yordan agya hunuu sɛ Israel mmarima adwane na Saulo ne ne mma atotɔ no, wɔgyaa nkuro no hɔ dwanedwanee, na Filistifoɔ no ba bɛtenaa mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ a Filistifoɔ ba bɛyiyii atɔfoɔ ho adeɛ no, wɔhunuu Saulo ne ne mma baasa no sɛ wɔatotɔ wɔ Gilboa bepɔ soɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔtwaa ne ti, na wɔyii ne ho akodeɛ, na wɔsoma maa wɔde kyinii Filistifoɔ asase so hyiae, sɛ wɔnkɔbɔ kaseɛ wɔ wɔn abosomfie ne ɔman no mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔde n’akodeɛ no kɔsiee Astarot dan mu, na ne funu no, wɔde sɛnee Bet-san fasuo ho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Yabes-gileadfoɔ tee deɛ Filistifoɔ ayɛ Saulo no,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> akofoɔ nyinaa sɔree nam anadwo nyinaa kɔfaa Saulo funu ne ne mma afunu no firii Bet-san fasuo no ho de baa Yabes, na wɔhyee no wɔ hɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔfaa wɔn nnompe kɔkoraa no santɛ dua no ase wɔ Yabes, na wɔdii mmuada nnanson."
		}
	}
};
